l-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Mission</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-mission\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms2.png\" title=\"Our Mission\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"grey-text\">Expanding Across West Africa:<br />\r\nSince our inception, Liquor Junction has expanded its footprint across West Africa, bringing the finest spirits closer to our valued customers. With a focus on accessibility and convenience, our chain of stores caters to the diverse tastes and preferences of the local community.<br />\r\nA Treasure Trove of Options:<br />\r\nStep into any Liquor Junction store, and you&#39;ll find yourself surrounded by a vast array of over 1500 products, including an extensive selection of beers, spirits, wines, and more. We take pride in offering something for every palate and occasion &ndash; from timeless classics to innovative new releases.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our&nbsp;Range</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-range\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Range\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore Our Diverse Range at Liquor Junction: Elevating Your Spirits Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Liquor Junction, we take pride in presenting a diverse and carefully curated range of beverages that caters to the varied tastes and preferences of our esteemed customers. Our extensive selection spans across categories, offering an unparalleled experience in the world of spirits.<br />\r\nAt Liquor Junction, our commitment to providing an expansive and high-quality range ensures that every visit is a journey of discovery. Step into our stores, where the world of beverages unfolds in all its richness, offering something exceptional for every taste and occasion. Cheers to a world of choices at Liquor Junction!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-range\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Range\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-future\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Future\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Future</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-future\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Future\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Shaping the Future of Spirits: The Vision of Liquor Junction</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As we stand at the forefront of the spirits industry, Liquor Junction envisions a future that is as dynamic and diverse as our extensive product range. Our commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction drives our vision for the years to come.<br />\r\nAt Liquor Junction, the future is an exciting journey of growth, sustainability, innovation, and community building. Join us on this adventure as we redefine the spirits retail landscape and continue to raise the bar for excellence in the industry. Cheers to a future filled with endless possibilities at Liquor Junction</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', '<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Company</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-company\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Company\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"grey-text\">Welcome to Liquor Junction &ndash; Your Ultimate Destination for Fine Spirits!<br />\r\nEstablished in 2021 by the visionary entrepreneur Sunny Punjabi, Liquor Junction has rapidly become West Africa&#39;s premier retail chain for all things spirits. With branches strategically scattered across the region, our commitment to providing an unparalleled selection of beverages has made us a favorite among discerning customers.<br />\r\nOur Founder, Sunny Punjabi:<br />\r\nAt the helm of Liquor Junction is Sunny Punjabi, a dynamic and passionate individual with a vision to redefine the liquor retail experience in West Africa. Sunny&#39;s dedication to curating a diverse and premium collection of beverages has laid the foundation for Liquor Junction&#39;s success.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-company\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Company\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-mission\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms2.png\" title=\"Our Mission\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Mission</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-mission\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms2.png\" title=\"Our Mission\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"grey-text\">Expanding Across West Africa:<br />\r\nSince our inception, Liquor Junction has expanded its footprint across West Africa, bringing the finest spirits closer to our valued customers. With a focus on accessibility and convenience, our chain of stores caters to the diverse tastes and preferences of the local community.<br />\r\nA Treasure Trove of Options:<br />\r\nStep into any Liquor Junction store, and you&#39;ll find yourself surrounded by a vast array of over 1500 products, including an extensive selection of beers, spirits, wines, and more. We take pride in offering something for every palate and occasion &ndash; from timeless classics to innovative new releases.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our&nbsp;Range</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-range\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Range\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore Our Diverse Range at Liquor Junction: Elevating Your Spirits Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At Liquor Junction, we take pride in presenting a diverse and carefully curated range of beverages that caters to the varied tastes and preferences of our esteemed customers. Our extensive selection spans across categories, offering an unparalleled experience in the world of spirits.<br />\r\nAt Liquor Junction, our commitment to providing an expansive and high-quality range ensures that every visit is a journey of discovery. Step into our stores, where the world of beverages unfolds in all its richness, offering something exceptional for every taste and occasion. Cheers to a world of choices at Liquor Junction!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-range\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Range\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-future\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Future\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Future</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-future\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Future\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Shaping the Future of Spirits: The Vision of Liquor Junction</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As we stand at the forefront of the spirits industry, Liquor Junction envisions a future that is as dynamic and diverse as our extensive product range. Our commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction drives our vision for the years to come.<br />\r\nAt Liquor Junction, the future is an exciting journey of growth, sustainability, innovation, and community building. Join us on this adventure as we redefine the spirits retail landscape and continue to raise the bar for excellence in the industry. Cheers to a future filled with endless possibilities at Liquor Junction</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2022-07-06 00:48:16', '2024-04-17 12:02:50'),
(2, NULL, NULL, 'Security & privacy', 'Sécurité et confidentialité', '<p>Your security and privacy are of paramount importance to us and we are committed to providing you with as safe and secure a shopping environment as possible. We understand the importance of keeping your personal and business information confidential. Any data you share with us is treated with the utmost sensitivity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All communication and data transmission between you and The Liquor Junction are encrypted to ensure that your information remains private and secure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you engage in financial transactions with us, rest assured that we utilize industry-standard security protocols to protect your payment information. Our payment processes are designed to meet the highest security standards, ensuring a safe and secure transaction environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Access to your account and personal information is restricted to authorized personnel only.</p>', '<p>Votre s&eacute;curit&eacute; et votre confidentialit&eacute; sont d&#39;une importance primordiale pour nous et nous nous engageons &agrave; vous offrir un environnement d&#39;achat aussi s&ucirc;r et s&eacute;curis&eacute; que possible. Nous comprenons l&rsquo;importance de garder vos informations personnelles et professionnelles confidentielles. Toutes les donn&eacute;es que vous partagez avec nous sont trait&eacute;es avec la plus grande sensibilit&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Toutes les communications et transmissions de donn&eacute;es entre vous et The Liquor Junction sont crypt&eacute;es pour garantir que vos informations restent priv&eacute;es et s&eacute;curis&eacute;es.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lorsque vous effectuez des transactions financi&egrave;res avec nous, soyez assur&eacute; que nous utilisons des protocoles de s&eacute;curit&eacute; conformes aux normes du secteur pour prot&eacute;ger vos informations de paiement. Nos processus de paiement sont con&ccedil;us pour r&eacute;pondre aux normes de s&eacute;curit&eacute; les plus &eacute;lev&eacute;es, garantissant ainsi un environnement de transaction s&ucirc;r et s&eacute;curis&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&#39;acc&egrave;s &agrave; votre compte et &agrave; vos informations personnelles est limit&eacute; au personnel autoris&eacute; uniquement.</p>', '<p>Your security and privacy are of paramount importance to us and we are committed to providing you with as safe and secure a shopping environment as possible. We understand the importance of keeping your personal and business information confidential. Any data you share with us is treated with the utmost sensitivity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All communication and data transmission between you and The Liquor Junction are encrypted to ensure that your information remains private and secure</p>\r\n\r\n<p>When you engage in financial transactions with us, rest assured that we utilize industry-standard security protocols to protect your payment information. Our payment processes are designed to meet the highest security standards, ensuring a safe and secure transaction environment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Access to your account and personal information is restricted to authorized personnel only.</p>', '<p>Votre s&eacute;curit&eacute; et votre confidentialit&eacute; sont d&#39;une importance primordiale pour nous et nous nous engageons &agrave; vous offrir un environnement d&#39;achat aussi s&ucirc;r et s&eacute;curis&eacute; que possible. Nous comprenons l&rsquo;importance de garder vos informations personnelles et professionnelles confidentielles. Toutes les donn&eacute;es que vous partagez avec nous sont trait&eacute;es avec la plus grande sensibilit&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Toutes les communications et transmissions de donn&eacute;es entre vous et The Liquor Junction sont crypt&eacute;es pour garantir que vos informations restent priv&eacute;es et s&eacute;curis&eacute;es.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lorsque vous effectuez des transactions financi&egrave;res avec nous, soyez assur&eacute; que nous utilisons des protocoles de s&eacute;curit&eacute; conformes aux normes du secteur pour prot&eacute;ger vos informations de paiement. Nos processus de paiement sont con&ccedil;us pour r&eacute;pondre aux normes de s&eacute;curit&eacute; les plus &eacute;lev&eacute;es, garantissant ainsi un environnement de transaction s&ucirc;r et s&eacute;curis&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&#39;acc&egrave;s &agrave; votre compte et &agrave; vos informations personnelles est limit&eacute; au personnel autoris&eacute; uniquement.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2022-07-06 00:49:00', '2024-02-02 13:35:04');
