(16, NULL, NULL, 'Placing Your Order', 'Passer votre commande', '<p><strong>Placing An Order</strong><br />\r\nSelecting &#39;Place Order&#39; will place your order. Within 24 hours of placing your order, you will receive an email confirming that your order has been received. We will also send you another email notifying you when your order has been shipped, details of our tracking number and confirmation that we have charged your credit card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Multiple Shipping Addresses</strong><br />\r\nUnfortunately, it is not possible to ship an order to multiple addresses. If you are shopping for people at different addresses you will have to place separate orders for each address, which will also be charged separately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gift Messages</strong><br />\r\nA personalised gift message service is available on all orders.</p>', '<p><strong>Passer une commande</strong><br />\r\nSelecting &#39;Place Order&#39; will place your order. Within 24 hours of placing your order, you will receive an email confirming that your order has been received. We will also send you another email notifying you when your order has been shipped, details of our tracking number and confirmation that we have charged your credit card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Plusieurs adresses de livraison</strong><br />\r\nUnfortunately, it is not possible to ship an order to multiple addresses. If you are shopping for people at different addresses you will have to place separate orders for each address, which will also be charged separately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Messages cadeaux</strong><br />\r\nA personalised gift message service is available on all orders.</p>', '<p><strong>Placing An Order</strong><br />\r\nSelecting &#39;Place Order&#39; will place your order. Within 24 hours of placing your order, you will receive an email confirming that your order has been received. We will also send you another email notifying you when your order has been shipped, details of our tracking number and confirmation that we have charged your credit card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Multiple Shipping Addresses</strong><br />\r\nUnfortunately, it is not possible to ship an order to multiple addresses. If you are shopping for people at different addresses you will have to place separate orders for each address, which will also be charged separately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Gift Messages</strong><br />\r\nA personalised gift message service is available on all orders.</p>', '<p><strong>Passer une commande</strong><br />\r\nSelecting &#39;Place Order&#39; will place your order. Within 24 hours of placing your order, you will receive an email confirming that your order has been received. We will also send you another email notifying you when your order has been shipped, details of our tracking number and confirmation that we have charged your credit card.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Plusieurs adresses de livraison</strong><br />\r\nUnfortunately, it is not possible to ship an order to multiple addresses. If you are shopping for people at different addresses you will have to place separate orders for each address, which will also be charged separately.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Messages cadeaux</strong><br />\r\nA personalised gift message service is available on all orders.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, '2023-09-21 09:43:22', '2024-02-02 13:28:40'),
(17, NULL, NULL, 'Payment options', 'Options de paiement', '<p>Payment for your order can be made using credit or debit card, by cash or by bank transfer. Payment can be made online using our automated checkout service, by telephone &ndash; to place your order by telephone, call us on 0555667788.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Credit or Debit Cards</strong><br />\r\nWe accept all major credit or debit cards.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Cash Payment</strong><br />\r\nCash payment can only be accepted for orders that will be collected. Collections need to be arranged in advance and can be made either from our Head Office.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Bank Transfer</strong><br />\r\nWe are happy to accept bank transfers.</p>', '<p>Le paiement de votre commande peut &ecirc;tre effectu&eacute; par carte de cr&eacute;dit ou de d&eacute;bit, en esp&egrave;ces ou par virement bancaire. Le paiement peut &ecirc;tre effectu&eacute; en ligne via notre service de paiement automatis&eacute;, par t&eacute;l&eacute;phone &ndash; pour passer votre commande par t&eacute;l&eacute;phone, appelez-nous au 0555667788.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Cartes de cr&eacute;dit ou de d&eacute;bit</strong><br />\r\nNous acceptons toutes les principales cartes de cr&eacute;dit ou de d&eacute;bit.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Paiement en esp&egrave;ces</strong><br />\r\nLe paiement en esp&egrave;ces ne peut &ecirc;tre accept&eacute; que pour les commandes qui seront retir&eacute;es. Les collectes doivent &ecirc;tre organis&eacute;es &agrave; l&rsquo;avance et peuvent &ecirc;tre effectu&eacute;es depuis notre si&egrave;ge social.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Virement</strong><br />\r\nNous acceptons volontiers les virements bancaires.</p>', '<p>Payment for your order can be made using credit or debit card, by cash or by bank transfer. Payment can be made online using our automated checkout service, by telephone &ndash; to place your order by telephone, call us on 0555667788.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Credit or Debit Cards</strong><br />\r\nWe accept all major credit or debit cards.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Cash Payment</strong><br />\r\nCash payment can only be accepted for orders that will be collected. Collections need to be arranged in advance and can be made either from our Head Office.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Bank Transfer</strong><br />\r\nWe are happy to accept bank transfers.</p>', '<p>Le paiement de votre commande peut &ecirc;tre effectu&eacute; par carte de cr&eacute;dit ou de d&eacute;bit, en esp&egrave;ces ou par virement bancaire. Le paiement peut &ecirc;tre effectu&eacute; en ligne via notre service de paiement automatis&eacute;, par t&eacute;l&eacute;phone &ndash; pour passer votre commande par t&eacute;l&eacute;phone, appelez-nous au 0555667788.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Cartes de cr&eacute;dit ou de d&eacute;bit</strong><br />\r\nNous acceptons toutes les principales cartes de cr&eacute;dit ou de d&eacute;bit.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Paiement en esp&egrave;ces</strong><br />\r\nLe paiement en esp&egrave;ces ne peut &ecirc;tre accept&eacute; que pour les commandes qui seront retir&eacute;es. Les collectes doivent &ecirc;tre organis&eacute;es &agrave; l&rsquo;avance et peuvent &ecirc;tre effectu&eacute;es depuis notre si&egrave;ge social.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong>Virement</strong><br />\r\nNous acceptons volontiers les virements bancaires.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, '2023-09-21 09:50:23', '2024-02-09 09:22:55'),
(18, NULL, '', 'Queries', 'Queries', '<p><strong>For all queries, we ask that you complete the support request form and our team will look into your query and get in touch with you.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo speed up our handling of your query, please ensure you include your order reference number. Our preference is to reply via email as this ensures we have a record of your queries for future reference. If you prefer for us to call you, please provide your contact details in your query.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease use this form form for :&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Amend your order.</li>\r\n	<li>Product related queries.</li>\r\n	<li>Technical queries.</li>\r\n	<li>General queries.</li>\r\n	<li>If any damage in product.</li>\r\n	<li>If received wrong or missing product.</li>\r\n	<li>Issue while tracking order.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>Pour toute question, nous vous demandons de remplir le formulaire de demande d&#39;assistance et notre &eacute;quipe examinera votre requ&ecirc;te et vous contactera.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nPour acc&eacute;l&eacute;rer notre traitement de votre demande, veuillez vous assurer d&#39;inclure votre num&eacute;ro de r&eacute;f&eacute;rence de commande. Notre pr&eacute;f&eacute;rence est de r&eacute;pondre par e-mail car cela garantit que nous avons un enregistrement de vos requ&ecirc;tes pour r&eacute;f&eacute;rence future. Si vous pr&eacute;f&eacute;rez que nous vous appelions, veuillez fournir vos coordonn&eacute;es dans votre requ&ecirc;te.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMerci d&#39;utiliser ce formulaire pour :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Modifiez votre commande.</li>\r\n	<li>Requ&ecirc;tes li&eacute;es au produit.</li>\r\n	<li>Requ&ecirc;tes techniques.</li>\r\n	<li>Requ&ecirc;tes g&eacute;n&eacute;rales.</li>\r\n	<li>En cas de dommage dans le produit.</li>\r\n	<li>Si re&ccedil;u un produit erron&eacute; ou manquant.</li>\r\n	<li>Probl&egrave;me lors du suivi de la commande.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>For all queries, we ask that you complete the support request form and our team will look into your query and get in touch with you.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nTo speed up our handling of your query, please ensure you include your order reference number. Our preference is to reply via email as this ensures we have a record of your queries for future reference. If you prefer for us to call you, please provide your contact details in your query.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease use this form form for :&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Amend your order.</li>\r\n	<li>Product related queries.</li>\r\n	<li>Technical queries.</li>\r\n	<li>General queries.</li>\r\n	<li>If any damage in product.</li>\r\n	<li>If received wrong or missing product.</li>\r\n	<li>Issue while tracking order.</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><strong>Pour toute question, nous vous demandons de remplir le formulaire de demande d&#39;assistance et notre &eacute;quipe examinera votre requ&ecirc;te et vous contactera.</strong><br />\r\n<br />\r\nPour acc&eacute;l&eacute;rer notre traitement de votre demande, veuillez vous assurer d&#39;inclure votre num&eacute;ro de r&eacute;f&eacute;rence de commande. Notre pr&eacute;f&eacute;rence est de r&eacute;pondre par e-mail car cela garantit que nous avons un enregistrement de vos requ&ecirc;tes pour r&eacute;f&eacute;rence future. Si vous pr&eacute;f&eacute;rez que nous vous appelions, veuillez fournir vos coordonn&eacute;es dans votre requ&ecirc;te.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMerci d&#39;utiliser ce formulaire pour :</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Modifiez votre commande.</li>\r\n	<li>Requ&ecirc;tes li&eacute;es au produit.</li>\r\n	<li>Requ&ecirc;tes techniques.</li>\r\n	<li>Requ&ecirc;tes g&eacute;n&eacute;rales.</li>\r\n	<li>En cas de dommage dans le produit.</li>\r\n	<li>Si re&ccedil;u un produit erron&eacute; ou manquant.</li>\r\n	<li>Probl&egrave;me lors du suivi de la commande.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, '2023-09-21 09:56:56', '2024-05-01 10:56:51'),
(19, NULL, NULL, 'Faq\'s', 'Faq\'s', '<p>Lorem Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry&#39;s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum.</p>', '<p>Lore<strong>m Ipsum is simply dummy text of the printing and typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been the industry&#39;s standard dummy text ever since the 1500s, when an unknown printer took a galley of type and scrambled it to make a type specimen book. It has survived not only five centuries, but also the leap into electronic typesetting, remaining essentially unchanged. It was popularised in the 1960s with the release of Letraset sheets containing Lorem Ipsum passages, and more recently with desktop publishing software like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem Ipsum</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, '2023-09-21 09:56:56', '2023-10-03 12:45:36'),
(21, NULL, NULL, 'Order By Phone', 'Commande par téléphone', '<p>If you would like help placing your order or would simply prefer to place your order by telephone please call us on the following number during office hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ghana Customers :&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:0555667788\"><span style=\"color:#0000CD;\"><u>0555667788</u></span></a><br />\r\n	Our Office is open between Monday to Saturday&nbsp; ( 9 AM - 11 PM )</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Sunday&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ( 9 AM - 00 AM Midnight)</p>', '<p>Si vous souhaitez de l&#39;aide pour passer votre commande ou pr&eacute;f&eacute;rez simplement passer votre commande par t&eacute;l&eacute;phone, veuillez nous appeler au num&eacute;ro suivant pendant les heures de bureau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Clients du Ghana : <a href=\"tel:0555667788\"><span style=\"color:#0000CD;\"><u>0555667788</u></span></a><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Notre bureau est ouvert du lundi au samedi&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (de 9h &agrave; 23h)<br />\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Dimanche&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (9h - 00 &agrave; minuit)</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>If you would like help placing your order or would simply prefer to place your order by telephone please call us on the following number during office hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ghana Customers :&nbsp;<a href=\"tel:0555667788\"><span style=\"color:#0000CD;\"><u>0555667788</u></span></a><br />\r\n	Our Office is open between Monday to Saturday&nbsp; ( 9 AM - 11 PM )</li>\r\n	<li>Sunday&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ( 11 AM - 11 PM )</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p>Si vous souhaitez de l&#39;aide pour passer votre commande ou pr&eacute;f&eacute;rez simplement passer votre commande par t&eacute;l&eacute;phone, veuillez nous appeler au num&eacute;ro suivant pendant les heures de bureau.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Clients du Ghana : <a href=\"tel:0555667788\"><span style=\"color:#0000CD;\"><u>0555667788</u></span></a><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	Notre bureau est ouvert du lundi au samedi&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (de 9h &agrave; 23h)</li>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;Dimanche&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; (11h - 23h 00)</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2023-10-28 07:16:00', '2024-03-12 11:55:51'),
(22, NULL, NULL, 'Trade Enquiries', 'Demandes commerciales', '<p class=\"body-large\">. <strong>Lorem </strong>Ipsum</p>', '<p class=\"body-large\">.</p>', '<p>. Lorem Ipsum</p>', '. Lorem Ipsum', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2023-10-28 07:17:26', '2024-02-02 13:26:00'),
(23, NULL, '', 'Press Enquiries', 'Les demandes de presse', '<p>For any press enquiry&nbsp;like filming or photography of stores, please contact our headoffice&nbsp;at <strong>sales@liquorjunction.com</strong>.</p>', '<p>Pour toute demande de presse comme un tournage ou une photographie de magasins, veuillez contacter notre si&egrave;ge social &agrave; <strong>sales@liquorjunction.com</strong>.</p>', '<p>For any press enquiry&nbsp;like filming or photography of stores, please contact our headoffice&nbsp;at&nbsp;<strong>sales@liquorjunction.com</strong>.</p>', '<p>Pour toute demande de presse comme un tournage ou une photographie de magasins, veuillez contacter notre si&egrave;ge social &agrave; <strong>sales@liquorjunction.com</strong>.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2023-10-28 07:19:06', '2024-05-01 10:26:24');
INSERT INTO `cms` (`id`, `language_id`, `photo`, `page_name`, `page_name_fr`, `page_content`, `page_content_fr`, `mobile_page_content`, `mobile_page_content_fr`, `title`, `body`, `image`, `create_by`, `update_by`, `status`, `remember_token`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(24, NULL, '', 'Our Company', 'Notre compagnie', '<section class=\"insurance py-100\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row align-items-center insurance-row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6 insurance-col\">\r\n<div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n	\r\n<h3>Our Company</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to Liquor Junction &ndash; Your Ultimate Destination for Fine\r\n	Spirits!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Established in 2021 by the visionary entrepreneur Sunny Punjabi,\r\n	Liquor Junction has rapidly become West Africa&#39;s premier retail\r\n	chain for all things spirits. With branches strategically scattered\r\n	across the region, our commitment to providing an unparalleled\r\n	selection of beverages has made us a favorite among discerning\r\n	customers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6 insurance-col\">\r\n	<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-company\"\r\n		src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\"\r\n		title=\"Our Company\" /></div>\r\n	<br>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"insurance py-100\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n	<div class=\"row align-items-center insurance-row\">\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6 insurance-col\">\r\n		<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-mission\"\r\n			src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms2.png\"\r\n			title=\"Our Mission\" /></div>\r\n			<br>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6 insurance-col\">\r\n		<div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n			\r\n		<h3>Our Mission</h3>\r\n		\r\n		<p style=\"color: rgb(133, 133, 132); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;text-align: justify;\">Since our inception, Liquor Junction has expanded its footprint across West Africa, bringing the finest spirits closer to our valued customers. With focus on accessibility and convenience, our chain of stores caters to the\r\n		diverse tastes and preferences of the local community.</p>\r\n		</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</section>\r\n\r\n\r\n<section class=\"insurance py-100\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n	<div class=\"row align-items-center insurance-row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6 insurance-col\">\r\n	<div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n		\r\n	<h3>Our Range</h3>\r\n	\r\n	<p\r\n	style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Explore Our Diverse Range at Liquor Junction: Elevating Your Spirits\r\n	Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p\r\n	style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;text-align: justify;\">\r\n	At Liquor Junction, we take pride in presenting a diverse and carefully\r\n	curated range of beverages that caters to the varied tastes and preferences\r\n	of our esteemed customers. Our extensive selection spans across categories,\r\n	offering an unparalleled experience in the world of spirits.<br\r\n		style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n	At Liquor Junction, our commitment to providing an expansive and\r\n	high-quality range ensures that every visit is a journey of discovery. Step\r\n	into our stores, where the world of beverages unfolds in all its richness,\r\n	offering something exceptional for every taste and occasion. Cheers to a\r\n	world of choices at Liquor Junction!</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6 insurance-col\">\r\n		<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-range\"\r\n			src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\"\r\n			title=\"Our Range\" /></div>\r\n			<br>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</section>\r\n\r\n	<section class=\"insurance py-100\">\r\n		<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"row align-items-center insurance-row\">\r\n		\r\n		\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-6 insurance-col\">\r\n			<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-future\"\r\n				src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms2.png\"\r\n				title=\"Our Future\" /></div>\r\n				<br>\r\n		</div>\r\n\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-6 insurance-col\">\r\n			<div class=\"content-inner\">\r\n				\r\n			<h3>Our Future</h3>\r\n			\r\n			<p\r\n												style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;text-align: justify;\">\r\n												Shaping the Future of Spirits: The Vision of Liquor Junction</p>\r\n	\r\n											<p\r\n												style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;text-align: justify;\">\r\n												As we stand at the forefront of the spirits industry, Liquor Junction\r\n												envisions a future that is as dynamic and diverse as our extensive product\r\n												range. Our commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction\r\n												drives our vision for the years to come.<br\r\n													style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n												<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n												At Liquor Junction, the future is an exciting journey of growth,\r\n												sustainability, innovation, and community building. Join us on this\r\n												adventure as we redefine the spirits retail landscape and continue to raise\r\n												the bar for excellence in the industry. Cheers to a future filled with\r\n												endless possibilities at Liquor Junction\r\n											</p>\r\n			</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n\r\n		</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		</section>\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n	\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Company</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-company\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Company\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to Liquor Junction &ndash; Your Ultimate Destination for Fine Spirits!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Established in 2021 by the visionary entrepreneur Sunny Punjabi, Liquor Junction has rapidly become West Africa&#39;s premier retail chain for all things spirits. With branches strategically scattered across the region, our commitment to providing an unparalleled selection of beverages has made us a favorite among discerning customers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-company\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Company\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-mission\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms2.png\" title=\"Our Mission\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Mission</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-mission\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms2.png\" title=\"Our Mission\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"grey-text\"><span style=\"color: rgb(133, 133, 132); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Expanding Across West Africa:</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(133, 133, 132); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Since our inception, Liquor Junction has expanded its footprint across West Africa, bringing the finest spirits closer to our valued customers. With a focus on accessibility and convenience, our chain of stores caters to the diverse tastes and preferences of the local community.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Range</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-range\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Range\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Explore Our Diverse Range at Liquor Junction: Elevating Your Spirits Experience</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">At Liquor Junction, we take pride in presenting a diverse and carefully curated range of beverages that caters to the varied tastes and preferences of our esteemed customers. Our extensive selection spans across categories, offering an unparalleled experience in the world of spirits.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\nAt Liquor Junction, our commitment to providing an expansive and high-quality range ensures that every visit is a journey of discovery. Step into our stores, where the world of beverages unfolds in all its richness, offering something exceptional for every taste and occasion. Cheers to a world of choices at Liquor Junction!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-range\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Range\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-future\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Future\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Future</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-future\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Future\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Shaping the Future of Spirits: The Vision of Liquor Junction</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">As we stand at the forefront of the spirits industry, Liquor Junction envisions a future that is as dynamic and diverse as our extensive product range. Our commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction drives our vision for the years to come.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\nAt Liquor Junction, the future is an exciting journey of growth, sustainability, innovation, and community building. Join us on this adventure as we redefine the spirits retail landscape and continue to raise the bar for excellence in the industry. Cheers to a future filled with endless possibilities at Liquor Junction</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', '<!-- Our Company -->\r\n<section class=\"cms py-60\">\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\r\n<div class=\"cms-content\">\r\n<h2>Our Company</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"cms-image\"><img alt=\"our-company\" src=\"https://liquorjunctionghana.com/assets/frontend/images/cms1.png\" title=\"Our Company\" /></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to Liquor Junction &ndash; Your Ultimate Destination for Fine Spirits!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Established in 2021 by the visionary entrepreneur Sunny Punjabi, Liquor Junction has rapidly become West Africa&#39;s premier retail chain for all things spirits. With branches strategically scattered across the region, our commitment to providing an unparalleled selection of beverages has made us a favorite among discerning customers.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<