rgin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Shaping the Future of Spirits: The Vision of Liquor Junction</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 18px;  color: rgb(133, 133, 132); padding-right: 30px; font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">As we stand at the forefront of the spirits industry, Liquor Junction envisions a future that is as dynamic and diverse as our extensive product range. Our commitment to excellence, innovation, and customer satisfaction drives our vision for the years to come.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\" />\r\nAt Liquor Junction, the future is an exciting journey of growth, sustainability, innovation, and community building. Join us on this adventure as we redefine the spirits retail landscape and continue to raise the bar for excellence in the industry. Cheers to a future filled with endless possibilities at Liquor Junction</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2023-10-31 05:52:33', '2024-02-13 08:55:52');
INSERT INTO `cms` (`id`, `language_id`, `photo`, `page_name`, `page_name_fr`, `page_content`, `page_content_fr`, `mobile_page_content`, `mobile_page_content_fr`, `title`, `body`, `image`, `create_by`, `update_by`, `status`, `remember_token`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(26, NULL, NULL, 'Responsible drinking', 'Consommation responsable', '<p><strong>Moderation:</strong><br />\r\nConsuming alcohol in moderation is key to minimizing the potential negative effects on physical and mental health. Excessive alcohol intake can lead to various health issues and increased risk of accidents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong><br />\r\nAbiding by the legal drinking age and following local laws and regulations regarding the sale and consumption of alcohol is crucial. Breaking these laws can result in legal consequences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Personal Health:</strong><br />\r\nBeing mindful of one&#39;s health and understanding any potential medical conditions or medications that may interact negatively with alcohol is important. Some individuals should avoid alcohol altogether due to health concerns.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Social Responsibility:</strong><br />\r\nIndividuals should be considerate of the impact of their drinking on others. This includes not causing harm to oneself or others, and being aware of the potential for alcohol-related violence, accidents, or disruptions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Designated Driving:</strong><br />\r\nIf someone chooses to drink, they should plan for a safe way to get home. This might involve having a designated driver, using public transportation, or arranging for a taxi or rideshare service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s essential for individuals to make informed and responsible choices about alcohol consumption, considering both their own well-being and the well-being of others. If someone struggles with alcohol misuse or addiction, seeking professional help and support is advisable.</p>', '<p><strong>Mod&eacute;ration:</strong><br />\r\nConsommer de l&rsquo;alcool avec mod&eacute;ration est essentiel pour minimiser les effets n&eacute;gatifs potentiels sur la sant&eacute; physique et mentale. Une consommation excessive d&#39;alcool peut entra&icirc;ner divers probl&egrave;mes de sant&eacute; et un risque accru d&#39;accidents.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Conformit&eacute; l&eacute;gale:</strong><br />\r\nIl est crucial de respecter l&rsquo;&acirc;ge l&eacute;gal pour consommer de l&rsquo;alcool et de suivre les lois et r&eacute;glementations locales concernant la vente et la consommation d&rsquo;alcool. Enfreindre ces lois peut entra&icirc;ner des cons&eacute;quences juridiques.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Sant&eacute; personnelle:</strong><br />\r\nIl est important d&#39;&ecirc;tre attentif &agrave; sa sant&eacute; et de comprendre tout probl&egrave;me de sant&eacute; potentiel ou tout m&eacute;dicament susceptible d&#39;interagir n&eacute;gativement avec l&#39;alcool. Certaines personnes devraient &eacute;viter compl&egrave;tement l&rsquo;alcool pour des raisons de sant&eacute;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Responsabilit&eacute; sociale:</strong><br />\r\nLes individus doivent &ecirc;tre attentifs &agrave; l&rsquo;impact de leur consommation d&rsquo;alcool sur les autres. Cela implique de ne pas se faire de mal &agrave; soi-m&ecirc;me ou &agrave; autrui et d&#39;&ecirc;tre conscient du potentiel de violence, d&#39;accidents ou de perturbations li&eacute;s &agrave; l&#39;alcool.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Conduite d&eacute;sign&eacute;e :</strong><br />\r\nSi quelqu&rsquo;un choisit de boire, il doit pr&eacute;voir un moyen s&ucirc;r de rentrer chez lui. Cela peut impliquer d&#39;avoir un chauffeur d&eacute;sign&eacute;, d&#39;utiliser les transports en commun ou de r&eacute;server un taxi ou un service de covoiturage.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIl est essentiel que les individus fassent des choix &eacute;clair&eacute;s et responsables en mati&egrave;re de consommation d&#39;alcool, en tenant compte &agrave; la fois de leur propre bien-&ecirc;tre et de celui des autres. Si une personne souffre d&rsquo;abus ou de d&eacute;pendance &agrave; l&rsquo;alcool, il est conseill&eacute; de demander l&rsquo;aide et le soutien d&rsquo;un professionnel.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>Moderation:</strong><br />\r\nConsuming alcohol in moderation is key to minimizing the potential negative effects on physical and mental health. Excessive alcohol intake can lead to various health issues and increased risk of accidents.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong><br />\r\nAbiding by the legal drinking age and following local laws and regulations regarding the sale and consumption of alcohol is crucial. Breaking these laws can result in legal consequences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Personal Health:</strong><br />\r\nBeing mindful of one&#39;s health and understanding any potential medical conditions or medications that may interact negatively with alcohol is important. Some individuals should avoid alcohol altogether due to health concerns.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Social Responsibility:</strong><br />\r\nIndividuals should be considerate of the impact of their drinking on others. This includes not causing harm to oneself or others, and being aware of the potential for alcohol-related violence, accidents, or disruptions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Designated Driving:</strong><br />\r\nIf someone chooses to drink, they should plan for a safe way to get home. This might involve having a designated driver, using public transportation, or arranging for a taxi or rideshare service.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It&#39;s essential for individuals to make informed and responsible choices about alcohol consumption, considering both their own well-being and the well-being of others. If someone struggles with alcohol misuse or addiction, seeking professional help and support is advisable.</p>', '<p><strong>Mod&eacute;ration:</strong><br />\r\nConsommer de l&rsquo;alcool avec mod&eacute;ration est essentiel pour minimiser les effets n&eacute;gatifs potentiels sur la sant&eacute; physique et mentale. Une consommation excessive d&#39;alcool peut entra&icirc;ner divers probl&egrave;mes de sant&eacute; et un risque accru d&#39;accidents.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Conformit&eacute; l&eacute;gale:</strong><br />\r\nIl est crucial de respecter l&rsquo;&acirc;ge l&eacute;gal pour consommer de l&rsquo;alcool et de suivre les lois et r&eacute;glementations locales concernant la vente et la consommation d&rsquo;alcool. Enfreindre ces lois peut entra&icirc;ner des cons&eacute;quences juridiques.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Sant&eacute; personnelle:</strong><br />\r\nIl est important d&#39;&ecirc;tre attentif &agrave; sa sant&eacute; et de comprendre tout probl&egrave;me de sant&eacute; potentiel ou tout m&eacute;dicament susceptible d&#39;interagir n&eacute;gativement avec l&#39;alcool. Certaines personnes devraient &eacute;viter compl&egrave;tement l&rsquo;alcool pour des raisons de sant&eacute;.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Responsabilit&eacute; sociale:</strong><br />\r\nLes individus doivent &ecirc;tre attentifs &agrave; l&rsquo;impact de leur consommation d&rsquo;alcool sur les autres. Cela implique de ne pas se faire de mal &agrave; soi-m&ecirc;me ou &agrave; autrui et d&#39;&ecirc;tre conscient du potentiel de violence, d&#39;accidents ou de perturbations li&eacute;s &agrave; l&#39;alcool.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Conduite d&eacute;sign&eacute;e :</strong><br />\r\nSi quelqu&rsquo;un choisit de boire, il doit pr&eacute;voir un moyen s&ucirc;r de rentrer chez lui. Cela peut impliquer d&#39;avoir un chauffeur d&eacute;sign&eacute;, d&#39;utiliser les transports en commun ou de r&eacute;server un taxi ou un service de covoiturage.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIl est essentiel que les individus fassent des choix &eacute;clair&eacute;s et responsables en mati&egrave;re de consommation d&#39;alcool, en tenant compte &agrave; la fois de leur propre bien-&ecirc;tre et de celui des autres. Si une personne souffre d&rsquo;abus ou de d&eacute;pendance &agrave; l&rsquo;alcool, il est conseill&eacute; de demander l&rsquo;aide et le soutien d&rsquo;un professionnel.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</