(42, '654b8aece52d7', 'PRO000042', 0, 'wine', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The wide variety of white wines comes from the large number of&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Varietal\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Varietal\">varieties</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">, methods of&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Winemaking\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Winemaking\">winemaking</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">, and ratios of&nbsp;</span><a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Residual_sugar\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Residual sugar\">residual sugar</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. White wine is mainly from &quot;white&quot; grapes, which are green or yellow in colour, such as the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chardonnay\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Chardonnay\">Chardonnay</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sauvignon_blanc\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Sauvignon blanc\">Sauvignon blanc</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Riesling\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Riesling\">Riesling</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">.</span></p>', 'White wine is a wine that is fermented without skin contact. The colour can be straw-yellow, yellow-green, or yellow-gold.', 9, '', NULL, 8, 11, '16994495802866.mp4', 'wine', 'White wine is a wine that is fermented without skin contact. The colour can be straw-yellow, yellow-green, or yellow-gold.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">The wide variety of white wines comes from the large number of&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Varietal\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Varietal\">varieties</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">, methods of&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Winemaking\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Winemaking\">winemaking</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">, and ratios of&nbsp;</span><a class=\"mw-redirect\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Residual_sugar\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Residual sugar\">residual sugar</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">. White wine is mainly from &quot;white&quot; grapes, which are green or yellow in colour, such as the&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chardonnay\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Chardonnay\">Chardonnay</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sauvignon_blanc\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Sauvignon blanc\">Sauvignon blanc</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;and&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Riesling\" style=\"text-decoration-line: none; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); background-image: none; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\" title=\"Riesling\">Riesling</a><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 34); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000001', 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-08 13:19:40', '2023-12-01 10:01:14'),
(43, '654b8c2101321', 'PRO000043', 0, 'Vodka', '<p>Vodka is a clear distilled alcoholic beverage. Different varieties originated in Poland, Russia, and Sweden. Vodka is composed mainly of water and ethanol but sometimes with traces of impurities and flavourings.</p>', 'Vodka is a clear distilled alcoholic beverage. Different varieties originated in Poland, Russia, and Sweden.', 10, '', NULL, 10, 12, '', 'Vodka', 'Vodka is a clear distilled alcoholic beverage. Different varieties originated in Poland, Russia, and Sweden.', '<p>Vodka is a clear distilled alcoholic beverage. Different varieties originated in Poland, Russia, and Sweden. Vodka is composed mainly of water and ethanol but sometimes with traces of impurities and flavourings.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000043', 0, 1, 2, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-08 13:24:49', '2023-12-01 10:01:46'),
(44, '654b8fc6bb3f2', 'PRO000044', 0, 'Beer', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Beer is one of the oldest types of alcoholic drinks in the world, and the most widely consumed.Beer is one of the oldest types of alcoholic drinks in the world, and the most widely consumed.Beer is one of the oldest types of alcoholic drinks in the world, and the most widely consumed.</span></p>', 'Beer is one of the oldest types of alcoholic drinks in the world, and the most widely consumed.', 11, '', NULL, 13, 11, '16994508223674.mp4', 'Beer', 'Beer is one of the oldest types of alcoholic drinks in the world, and the most widely consumed.', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Beer is one of the oldest types of alcoholic drinks in the world, and the most widely consumed.Beer is one of the oldest types of alcoholic drinks in the world, and the most widely consumed.Beer is one of the oldest types of alcoholic drinks in the world, and the most widely consumed.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000044', 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-08 13:40:22', '2024-05-07 09:21:53'),
(45, '654b90fce3b49', 'PRO000045', 0, 'Red wine', '<p>Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.</p>', 'Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.', 10, '', NULL, 10, 12, '', 'Red wine', 'Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.', '<p>Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.Red wine is a type of wine made from dark-colored grape varieties.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000045', 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-08 13:45:32', '2023-12-01 10:01:46'),
(46, '6555fec80f36a', 'PRO000046', 0, 'Monin Mojito Mint Sirup', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:\r\n collapse;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt\">\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">&nbsp;MONIN Mojito Mint is&nbsp;a refreshing mint and lime flavour that can be used beyond the bar in countless non-alcoholic applications. Also suitable as flavouring syrup for SodaStream and other soda makers. Sugar, water, natural mint aroma.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Mild mint aroma, refreshing and sweet herbal mint flavor with a citrus accent', 12, '', NULL, 14, 14, '', 'Monin Mojito Menthe Sirop', 'Arôme de menthe doux, saveur de menthe à base de plantes rafraîchissante et sucrée avec un accent d\'agrumes', '<p>MONIN Mojito Mint est une saveur rafra&icirc;chissante de menthe et de citron vert qui peut &ecirc;tre utilis&eacute;e au-del&agrave; du bar dans d&#39;innombrables applications sans alcool. Convient &eacute;galement comme sirop aromatisant pour SodaStream et autres fabricants de soda. Sucre, eau, ar&ocirc;me naturel de menthe.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000046', 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-16 11:36:40', '2023-11-30 04:23:40'),
(47, '6556000b96be1', 'PRO000047', 0, 'Monin Grenadine Sirup', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:\r\n collapse;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt\">\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">Monin Grenadine, 1 Ltr. Grenadine is the most common ingredient used for flavouring purpose in the classic bar mixology. Monin Grenadine comes in a nice red colour.&nbsp;It contains flavour of red berries with a touch of vanilla.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'his distinctive red syrup is full of red berry notes with a hit of vanilla.', 12, '', NULL, 14, 14, '', 'Monin Grenadine Sirup', 'son sirop rouge distinctif regorge de notes de fruits rouges avec une touche de vanille.', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:\r\n collapse;width:220pt\" width=\"293\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt\">\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:220pt\" width=\"293\">Monin Grenadine, 1 litre. La grenadine est l&rsquo;ingr&eacute;dient le plus couramment utilis&eacute; &agrave; des fins aromatisantes dans la mixologie classique des barres. Monin Grenadine se pr&eacute;sente dans une jolie couleur rouge. Il contient des ar&ocirc;mes de fruits rouges avec une touche de vanille.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000047', 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-16 11:42:03', '2023-11-30 04:23:40'),
(48, '6556005d3c60e', 'PRO000048', 0, 'Monin Lemon Tea Sirup', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:\r\n collapse;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt\">\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">Monin&nbsp;Lemon Tea syrup&nbsp;contains a high concentration of crisp, tart lemon and black tea and is pre-sweetened with pure cane sugar. The easiest, most convenient way to create refreshing lemon tea beverages. Comes in a 700ml 100% recyclable glass bottle.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Syrup with taste of lemon tea to create authentic, refreshing iced teas', 12, '', NULL, 14, 14, '', 'Monin Lemon Tea Sirup', 'Sirop au goût de thé au citron pour créer des thés glacés authentiques et rafraîchissants', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:\r\n collapse;width:220pt\" width=\"293\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt\">\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:220pt\" width=\"293\">Le sirop de th&eacute; au citron Monin&nbsp;contient une forte concentration de citron croquant et acidul&eacute; et de th&eacute; noir et est pr&eacute;-sucr&eacute; avec du sucre de canne pur. Le moyen le plus simple et le plus pratique de cr&eacute;er des boissons rafra&icirc;chissantes au th&eacute; au citron. Livr&eacute; dans une bouteille en verre 100% recyclable de 700 ml.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000048', 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-16 11:43:25', '2023-11-30 04:23:40'),
(49, '65560238428a5', 'PRO000049', 0, 'Monin Peach Tea Syrup', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:\r\n collapse;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt\">\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">Create deliciously refreshing peach iced tea beverages with Monin peach tea syrup. Conveniently pre-sweetened with pure cane sugar and highly concentrated &ndash; just add water and serve iced. Comes in a 700ml 100% recyclable glass bottle.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:802pt\" width=\"1070\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'MONIN Peach Tea syrup with intense fruit flavours packs a powerful fruity punch and marries perfectly with the naturally astringent', 12, '', NULL, 14, 14, '', 'Monin Peach Tea Syrup', 'Le sirop de thé à la pêche MONIN aux saveurs de fruits intenses contient un puissant punch fruité et se marie parfaitement avec l\'astringent naturel.', '<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:\r\n collapse;width:220pt\" width=\"293\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt\">\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:220pt\" width=\"293\">Cr&eacute;ez des boissons au th&eacute; glac&eacute; &agrave; la p&ecirc;che d&eacute;licieusement rafra&icirc;chissantes avec le sirop de th&eacute; &agrave; la p&ecirc;che Monin. Id&eacute;alement pr&eacute;-sucr&eacute; avec du sucre de canne pur et hautement concentr&eacute; &ndash; il suffit d&rsquo;ajouter de l&rsquo;eau et de servir glac&eacute;. Livr&eacute; dans une bouteille en verre 100% recyclable de 700 ml.</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td class=\"xl65\" height=\"19\" style=\"height:14.4pt;width:220pt\" width=\"293\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000049', 0, 1, 2, NULL, NULL, '2023-11-16 11:51:20', '2023-11-30 04:23:40'),
