(398, '65ca0a7cbaa33', 'PRO000398', 0, 'San Pellegrino Sparkling Water', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">San Pellegrino is&nbsp;high in mineral content - mostly Calcium, Magnesium, Bicarbonate, Chloride, and Sulphate. The extremely low Nitrate level is perhaps San Pellegrino&#39;s greatest virtue</span></p>', 'Crisp and clean taste pairs well with any meal,Zero calories, low sodium, and no artificial colours or flavours.', 25, '', NULL, 44, 54, '', 'San Pellegrino Sparkling Water', 'Le goût net et net se marie bien avec n\'importe quel repas. Zéro calories, faible teneur en sodium et sans colorants ni arômes artificiels.', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">San Pellegrino est&nbsp;riche en min&eacute;raux&nbsp;: principalement du calcium, du magn&eacute;sium, du bicarbonate, du chlorure et du sulfate. Le niveau de nitrate extr&ecirc;mement bas est peut-&ecirc;tre la plus grande vertu de San Pellegrino.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000398', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-02-12 12:09:32', '2024-05-14 13:18:56'),
