(400, '6644b8deaa99c', 'PRO000400', 0, 'The Macallan 18 Yrs Double Cask 43%', '<p>The Macallan Double Cask 43% 18 Yrs, a perfectly balanced single malt whisky matured for 18 yrs in both American and European sherry seasoned oak casks. Sherry seasoned American oak adds delicate vanilla to the subtle spice of European oak, delivering a whisky with a sweeter, warmer taste and character</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Macallan 18 Yrs&nbsp;Double Cask 2022 Release 43% - Made by blending 18 yrs whisky from European and American oak casks, both of which are seasoned with sherry, this is a warming, sweet single malt and the pinnacle of Macallan&#39;s Double Cask range. Cask No.</p>', 'Macallan 18 Year Old Double Cask 2022 Release 43% - Made by blending 18 yrs whisky from European and American oak', 15, '', NULL, 35, 60, '', 'The Macallan 18 Yrs Double Cask 43%', 'Macallan 18 ans Double Cask 2022 Release 43% - Fabriqué en mélangeant du whisky de 18 ans à partir de chênes européens et américains', '<p>Le Macallan Double Cask 18 ans, un whisky single malt parfaitement &eacute;quilibr&eacute;, vieilli pendant 18 ans dans des f&ucirc;ts de ch&ecirc;ne assaisonn&eacute;s de sherry am&eacute;ricain et europ&eacute;en. Le ch&ecirc;ne am&eacute;ricain assaisonn&eacute; au sherry ajoute une vanille d&eacute;licate aux &eacute;pices subtiles du ch&ecirc;ne europ&eacute;en, offrant ainsi un whisky au go&ucirc;t et au caract&egrave;re plus doux et plus chaleureux.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Macallan 18 ans Double Cask 2022 version 43 % - Fabriqu&eacute; en m&eacute;langeant du whisky de 18 ans d&#39;&acirc;ge &agrave; partir de f&ucirc;ts de ch&ecirc;ne europ&eacute;en et am&eacute;ricain, tous deux assaisonn&eacute;s avec du sherry, il s&#39;agit d&#39;un single malt chaleureux et doux et le summum du Double Cask de Macallan. gamme. Num&eacute;ro de f&ucirc;t</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000400', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-15 13:30:06', '2024-06-11 09:05:21'),
(401, '6644de197ea7c', 'PRO000401', 0, 'Glenfiddich 12 Yrs', '<p>Flowing in the Valley of the Deer since 1887, the family&#39;s signature expression is the world&#39;s most awarded single malt Scotch whisky. With a unique freshness from the same Highland spring water they&#39;ve used since 1887, its distinctive fruitiness comes from the high cut point William Grant always insisted upon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Glenfiddich 12 Year Old single malt Scotch whisky is the ideal spirit for lovers of everyday luxury, this single malt delivers distinctively fresh and fruity notes with a hint of pear and develops into butterscotch, cream, malt and subtle oak flavors. Skillfully crafted. Enjoy responsibly.</p>', 'Glenfiddich 12 Year Old single malt Scotch whisky is the ideal spirit for lovers of everyday luxury. Enjoy responsibly.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 34, '', 'Glenfiddich 12 Yrs', 'Le whisky écossais single malt Glenfiddich 12 ans d\'âge est le spiritueux idéal pour les amateurs de luxe au quotidien.', '<p>Coulant dans la Vall&eacute;e des Cerfs depuis 1887, l&#39;expression signature de la famille est le whisky &eacute;cossais single malt le plus prim&eacute; au monde. Avec une fra&icirc;cheur unique provenant de la m&ecirc;me eau de source des Highlands qu&#39;ils utilisent depuis 1887, son fruit&eacute; distinctif vient du point de coupe &eacute;lev&eacute; sur lequel William Grant a toujours insist&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Le whisky &eacute;cossais single malt Glenfiddich 12 ans d&#39;&acirc;ge est le spiritueux id&eacute;al pour les amateurs de luxe au quotidien. Ce single malt d&eacute;livre des notes distinctement fra&icirc;ches et fruit&eacute;es avec une pointe de poire et se d&eacute;veloppe sur des saveurs de caramel &eacute;cossais, de cr&egrave;me, de malt et de subtiles saveurs de ch&ecirc;ne. Habilement con&ccedil;u. Profitez de mani&egrave;re responsable.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000401', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-15 16:08:57', '2024-06-10 18:18:57'),
(402, '6644e6537d4d1', 'PRO000402', 0, 'Glenfiddich 15 Yrs', '<p>The richly layered Glenfiddich 15 Year Old single malt Scotch whisky is innovatively matured in three types of oak cask: sherry, bourbon and new oak, before being married in thier unique, handcrafted Oregon pine Solera vat. Year on year, this Solera vat is never emptied but is always kept at least half full creating a deliciously harmonious and intense whisky which gets more complex and intriguing every year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speyside, Scotland- Glenfiddich Solera Reserve Scotch Whisky is a warm and spicy single malt matured for 15 years in bourbon, new oak and sherry casks before harmonizing in our unique Solera vat.</p>', 'Speyside, Scotland- Glenfiddich Solera Reserve Scotch Whisky is a warm and spicy single malt matured for 15 years', 15, '', NULL, 35, 34, '', 'Glenfiddich 15 Yrs', 'Speyside, Écosse - Le whisky écossais Glenfiddich Solera Reserve est un single malt chaud et épicé mûri pendant 15 ans en fûts', '<p>Le whisky &eacute;cossais single malt Glenfiddich 15 ans d&#39;&acirc;ge, richement &eacute;tag&eacute;, est vieilli de mani&egrave;re innovante dans trois types de f&ucirc;ts de ch&ecirc;ne : sherry, bourbon et ch&ecirc;ne neuf, avant d&#39;&ecirc;tre mari&eacute; dans leur cuve Solera unique en pin d&#39;Oregon, fabriqu&eacute;e &agrave; la main. Ann&eacute;e apr&egrave;s ann&eacute;e, cette cuve Solera n&#39;est jamais vid&eacute;e mais est toujours conserv&eacute;e au moins &agrave; moiti&eacute; pleine, cr&eacute;ant un whisky d&eacute;licieusement harmonieux et intense qui devient chaque ann&eacute;e plus complexe et intrigant.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Speyside, &Eacute;cosse - Le whisky &eacute;cossais Glenfiddich Solera Reserve est un single malt chaud et &eacute;pic&eacute; m&ucirc;ri pendant 15 ans en f&ucirc;ts de bourbon, de ch&ecirc;ne neuf et de sherry avant de s&#39;harmoniser dans notre cuve Solera unique.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000402', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-15 16:44:03', '2024-06-10 17:51:52'),
(403, '6645dda4aa020', 'PRO000403', 0, 'Grants Tripple Wood Stand FAST', '<p>William Grant&#39;s Grant&#39;s Triple Wood Stand Fast Blended Scotch Whisky 43% 1L. Consist: Nose: Smooth and sweet with elegant layers of honeycomb and spice. Taste: Notes of dried fruits and oak playfully combine with vanilla and cinnamon.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'William Grant\'s Grant\'s Triple Wood Stand Fast Blended Scotch Whisky 43% 1L.', 15, '', NULL, 48, 127, '', 'Grants Tripple Wood Stand FAST', 'William Grant\'s Grant\'s Triple Wood Stand Fast Blended Scotch Whisky 43% 1L.', '<p>William Grant&#39;s Grant&#39;s Triple Wood Stand Fast Blended Scotch Whisky 43% 1L. Composition : Nez : Doux et doux avec d&#39;&eacute;l&eacute;gantes couches de nid d&#39;abeille et d&#39;&eacute;pices. Go&ucirc;t : Des notes de fruits secs et de ch&ecirc;ne se combinent de mani&egrave;re ludique avec la vanille et la cannelle.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000403', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-16 10:19:16', '2024-05-28 13:47:22'),
(404, '6648a81aee0e4', 'PRO000404', 0, 'Glenmorangie The Original 10 Yrs', '<p>The original expression of our elegant, floral spirit and the real backbone of the Glenmorangie range. A ten-year-old single malt, Glenmorangie Original is produced by marrying the delicate spirit that emerges from Scotland&#39;s tallest stills, with first and second fill American white oak casks.</p>', 'The original expression of our elegant, floral spirit and the real backbone of the Glenmorangie range.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 35, '', 'Glenmorangie The Original 10 Yrs', 'L\'expression originale de notre esprit élégant et floral et véritable colonne vertébrale de la gamme Glenmorangie.', '<p>L&#39;expression originale de notre esprit &eacute;l&eacute;gant et floral et v&eacute;ritable colonne vert&eacute;brale de la gamme Glenmorangie. Single malt &acirc;g&eacute; de dix ans, Glenmorangie Original est produit en mariant l&#39;alcool d&eacute;licat qui &eacute;merge des plus hauts alambics d&#39;&Eacute;cosse avec des f&ucirc;ts de ch&ecirc;ne blanc am&eacute;ricain de premier et de deuxi&egrave;me remplissage.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000404', 0, 0, 2, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-18 13:07:38', '2024-06-11 09:20:00'),
(405, '664b42711f0ac', 'PRO000405', 0, 'Claymore Blended Scotch Whisky', '<p>The Claymore blended Scotch Whisky is aged between four to five years in strictly selected barrels. This maturation imparts its special character and created the beautiful mahogany color of this Scotch. When poured into a glass a complex variety of scents escape.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is a powerful sangria, with a touch of carbonic gas that gives it a refreshing character. It has intense aromas of red fruits, typical of wine, mixed with citrus notes and a touch of cinnamon.</p>', 'The Claymore blended Scotch Whisky is aged between four to five years in strictly selected barrels.', 15, '', NULL, 48, 147, '', 'Claymore Blended Scotch Whisky', 'Le Claymore Blended Scotch Whisky est vieilli entre quatre et cinq ans dans des fûts strictement sélectionnés.', '<p>Le Claymore Blended Scotch Whisky est vieilli entre quatre et cinq ans dans des f&ucirc;ts strictement s&eacute;lectionn&eacute;s. Cette maturation conf&egrave;re son caract&egrave;re particulier et cr&eacute;e la belle couleur acajou de ce Scotch. Lorsqu&#39;on le verse dans un verre, une vari&eacute;t&eacute; complexe de parfums s&#39;&eacute;chappent.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&#39;est une sangria puissante, avec une touche de gaz carbonique qui lui conf&egrave;re un caract&egrave;re rafra&icirc;chissant. Il pr&eacute;sente des ar&ocirc;mes intenses de fruits rouges, typiques du vin, m&ecirc;l&eacute;s &agrave; des notes d&#39;agrumes et une touche de cannelle.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000405', 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-20 12:30:41', '2024-05-28 13:47:26'),
(406, '664b4501e4400', 'PRO000406', 0, 'Cardhu 12yrs', '<p>Cardhu 12 Year Old is a luxury single malt Scotch Whisky from Lower Speyside, Scotland produced in limited quantities by a deliberately slow distillation process and then matured for 12 years. The reward of affording all this time is a delectable whisky of an exceptionally smooth and mellow character.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Orchard fruits of apple and pear, rich with good body. Taste: Gentle on the palate, soft peat smoke, fruity sweetness and malted barley. Finish: Long and smooth with some dried fruits and subtle smoke.</p>', 'Cardhu 12 Year Old is a luxury single malt Scotch Whisky from Lower Speyside, Scotland', 15, '', NULL, 35, 26, '', 'Cardhu 12yrs', 'Cardhu 12 ans est un whisky écossais single malt de luxe du Lower Speyside, en Écosse.', '<p>Cardhu 12 ans est un whisky &eacute;cossais single malt de luxe du Lower Speyside, en &Eacute;cosse, produit en quantit&eacute;s limit&eacute;es par un processus de distillation d&eacute;lib&eacute;r&eacute;ment lent, puis vieilli pendant 12 ans. La r&eacute;compense de tout ce temps est un d&eacute;licieux whisky au caract&egrave;re exceptionnellement doux et moelleux.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fruits du verger de pomme et de poire, riches avec un bon corps. Go&ucirc;t : Doux en bouche, fum&eacute;e tourb&eacute;e douce, douceur fruit&eacute;e et orge malt&eacute;e. Finale : Longue et douce avec quelques fruits secs et une fum&eacute;e subtile.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000406', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-20 12:41:37', '2024-06-10 17:35:59'),
(407, '664b5ad7c1e19', 'PRO000407', 0, 'Dewars 12 yrs Blended Scotch Whisky', '<p>Dewar&#39;s 12&nbsp;Year Old Blended Scotch Whisky is a blend of very rare vintage single malt and single grain Scotch whiskies, hence the nickname, &ldquo;The Vintage.&rdquo; Each bottle includes whiskies from the five single malt distilleries owned by John Dewar and Sons. The whiskies are then married in vintage oak casks. This special blend is creamy with notes of honey and marzipan. A masterpiece of Dewar&#39;s&reg; Master Blender Tom Aitken, Dewar&#39;s 18 Year Old Founders Reserve Scotch Whisky is a creamy, full and well-rounded blended whisky. This blended scotch whisky is laced with a rich body of dark chocolate flavor, and a dried fruit finish. Finished in selected oak casks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Dewar\'s 12 Year Old Blended Scotch Whisky is a blend of very rare vintage single malt', 15, '', NULL, 48, 148, '', 'Dewars 12 yrs Blended Scotch Whisky', 'Le Blended Scotch Whe malt et single grain vintage très rares, isky Dewar\'s 12 ans d\'âge est un mélange de whiskies écossais', '<p>Le Blended Scotch Whe malt et single grain vintage tr&egrave;s rares,&nbsp;isky Dewar&#39;s 12&nbsp;ans d&#39;&acirc;ge est un m&eacute;lange de whiskies &eacute;cossais singld&#39;o&ugrave; le surnom de &laquo; The Vintage &raquo;. Chaque bouteille comprend des whiskies provenant des cinq distilleries de single malt appartenant &agrave; John Dewar and Sons. Les whiskies sont ensuite mari&eacute;s dans des f&ucirc;ts de ch&ecirc;ne mill&eacute;sim&eacute;s. Ce m&eacute;lange sp&eacute;cial est cr&eacute;meux avec des notes de miel et de p&acirc;te d&#39;amande. Un chef-d&#39;&oelig;uvre du ma&icirc;tre m&eacute;langeur Dewar&#39;s&reg; Tom Aitken, le whisky &eacute;cossais Dewar&#39;s Founders Reserve &acirc;g&eacute; de 18 ans est un whisky m&eacute;lang&eacute; cr&eacute;meux, plein et bien rond. Ce whisky &eacute;cossais m&eacute;lang&eacute; est agr&eacute;ment&eacute; d&#39;un riche corps de saveur de chocolat noir et d&#39;une finale de fruits secs. Fini en f&ucirc;ts de ch&ecirc;ne s&eacute;lectionn&eacute;s.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000407', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-20 14:14:47', '2024-05-28 13:47:06'),
(408, '664b67a779970', 'PRO000408', 0, 'Gold Bar Premium Blended Whisky', '<p>Original is a smooth, award-winning American whiskey distilled from 88% corn, 9% rye and 3% barley then double casked in Napa Valley Wine Barrels. Gentle body with notes of honey, red fruit and subtle spice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Slightly sweet, with notes of vanilla, rye, honey and apple. PALATE: Starts with spice and apples with fresh citrus balanced off with honey. Light-bodied and gentle. FINISH: Smooth and balanced with no roughness or bitterness.</p>', 'Original is a smooth, award-winning American whiskey distilled from 88% corn, 9% rye and 3% barley then double casked', 15, '', NULL, 48, 149, '', 'Gold Bar Premium Blended Whisky', 'Original est un whisky américain doux et primé distillé à partir de 88 % de maïs, 9 % de seigle et 3 % d\'orge,', '<p>Original est un whisky am&eacute;ricain doux et prim&eacute; distill&eacute; &agrave; partir de 88 % de ma&iuml;s, 9 % de seigle et 3 % d&#39;orge, puis mis en double f&ucirc;t dans des f&ucirc;ts de vin de Napa Valley. Corps doux avec des notes de miel, de fruits rouges et d&#39;&eacute;pices subtiles.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&eacute;g&egrave;rement sucr&eacute;, avec des notes de vanille, de seigle, de miel et de pomme. BOUCHE : Commence sur des notes d&#39;&eacute;pices et de pommes avec des agrumes frais &eacute;quilibr&eacute;s par du miel. L&eacute;ger et doux. FINALE : Douce et &eacute;quilibr&eacute;e, sans rugosit&eacute; ni amertume.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000408', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-20 15:09:27', '2024-05-28 13:47:00'),
(409, '664b7311e5ffa', 'PRO000409', 0, 'Glengoyne Highland Single Malt Scotch Whisky 10yrs', '<p>Glengoyne is a distillery like no other. Taking its name from the glen in which it sits. &ndash; &lsquo;Glen Guin&rsquo; or &lsquo;Glen of the Wild Geese&rsquo; &ndash; it is hghly regarded as Scotland&rsquo;s most beautiful distillery. Residing close to Loch Lomond and the Trossachs National Park &ndash; nestled into Dumgoyne Hill. Six guiding pricinciples keep us true to our past, true to our taste. To change just one element would be to alter the bold, complex flavours of Glengoyne.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fresh green apples, toffee and a hint of nuttiness. This is the taste of distilling slower than anyone else in Scotland, of barley we dry by air &ndash; never peat &ndash; and of hand-selected sherry casks crafted from European and American oak.</p>', 'Glengoyne is a distillery like no other. Taking its name from the glen in which it sits.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 150, '', 'Glengoyne Highland Single Malt Scotch Whisky 10yrs', 'Glengoyne est une distillerie pas comme les autres. Tirant son nom du vallon dans lequel il se trouve.', '<p>Glengoyne est une distillerie pas comme les autres. Tirant son nom du vallon dans lequel il se trouve. &ndash; &laquo; Glen Guin &raquo; ou &laquo; Glen of the Wild Geese &raquo; &ndash; elle est consid&eacute;r&eacute;e comme la plus belle distillerie d&rsquo;&Eacute;cosse. R&eacute;sidant &agrave; proximit&eacute; du Loch Lomond et du parc national des Trossachs &ndash; nich&eacute; dans Dumgoyne Hill. Six principes directeurs nous maintiennent fid&egrave;les &agrave; notre pass&eacute;, fid&egrave;les &agrave; nos go&ucirc;ts. Changer un seul &eacute;l&eacute;ment reviendrait &agrave; modifier les saveurs audacieuses et complexes de Glengoyne.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pommes vertes fra&icirc;ches, caramel et un soup&ccedil;on de noisette. C&#39;est le go&ucirc;t d&#39;une distillation plus lente que quiconque en &Eacute;cosse, de l&#39;orge que nous s&eacute;chons &agrave; l&#39;air &ndash; jamais de tourbe &ndash; et de f&ucirc;ts de x&eacute;r&egrave;s s&eacute;lectionn&eacute;s &agrave; la main et fabriqu&eacute;s &agrave; partir de ch&ecirc;ne europ&eacute;en et am&eacute;ricain.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000409', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-20 15:58:09', '2024-06-10 17:32:45');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `uniqid`, `product_item_id`, `supplier_id`, `product_name`, `description`, `short_description`, `category_id`, `product_image`, `images`, `subcategory_id`, `brand_id`, `video`, `product_name_fr`, `short_description_fr`, `page_content_fr`, `product_qty`, `tech_data_sheet`, `retail_price`, `discount_price`, `is_admin_approve`, `most_view`, `is_product_bestseller`, `sku`, `average_rating`, `offer`, `status`, `in_store`, `in_online`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(410, '664b96617b572', 'PRO000410', 0, 'Monin Peach Tea Sirup', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif;\">Syrup with taste of lemon tea to create authentic, refreshing iced teas</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"hidden-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Outfit, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(133, 133, 132);\">Monin Lemon Tea syrup contains a high concentration of crisp, tart lemon and black tea and is pre-sweetened with pure cane sugar. The easiest, most convenient way to create refreshing lemon tea beverages. Comes in a 700ml 100% recyclable glass bottle.</p>\r\n</div>', 'Syrup with taste of lemon tea to create authentic, refreshing iced teas', 25, '', NULL, 47, 14, '', 'Monin Peach Tea Sirup', 'Sirop au goût de thé au citron pour créer des thés glacés authentiques et rafraîchissants', '<p>Sirop au go&ucirc;t de th&eacute; au citron pour cr&eacute;er des th&eacute;s glac&eacute;s authentiques et rafra&icirc;chissants</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Le sirop de th&eacute; au citron Monin contient une forte concentration de citron croquant et acidul&eacute; et de th&eacute; noir et est pr&eacute;-sucr&eacute; avec du sucre de canne pur. Le moyen le plus simple et le plus pratique de cr&eacute;er des boissons rafra&icirc;chissantes au th&eacute; au citron. Livr&eacute; dans une bouteille en verre 100% recyclable de 700 ml.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 'LQ000410', 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-20 18:28:49', '2024-05-28 13:46:38'),
(411, '6655fe4caf030', 'PRO000411', 0, 'Bruichladdich The Classic Laddie Scottish Whisky', '<p><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(235, 235, 245, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Bruichladdich Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; background-color: rgb(15, 15, 16);\">Our signature bottling and the definitive Bruichladdich. Showcasing the classic, floral and elegant Bruichladdich house style, The Classic Laddie is made from 100% Scottish barley, trickle distilled, non-chill filtered and colouring free.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(235, 235, 245, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Bruichladdich Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; background-color: rgb(15, 15, 16); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Sales of our 20cl Classic Laddie will be sold using&nbsp;our older&nbsp;bottle style.</span></p>', 'Our signature bottling and the definitive Bruichladdich. Showcasing the classic, floral and elegant Bruichladdich house style,', 15, '', NULL, 35, 151, '', 'BRUICHLADDICH THE CLASSIC LADDIE SCOTTISH WHISKY', 'Our signature bottling and the definitive Bruichladdich. Showcasing the classic, floral and elegant Bruichladdich house style,', '<p><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(235, 235, 245, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Bruichladdich Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; background-color: rgb(15, 15, 16);\">Our signature bottling and the definitive Bruichladdich. Showcasing the classic, floral and elegant Bruichladdich house style, The Classic Laddie is made from 100% Scottish barley, trickle distilled, non-chill filtered and colouring free.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(235, 235, 245, 0.8); font-family: &quot;Bruichladdich Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.4px; background-color: rgb(15, 15, 16); text-decoration-line: underline;\">Sales of our 20cl Classic Laddie will be sold using&nbsp;our older&nbsp;bottle style.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000411', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 15:54:52', '2024-06-10 17:29:29'),
(412, '665600a7698dc', 'PRO000412', 0, 'Glenfiddich 26 Years', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Speyside&#39;s Glenfiddich Distillery looked to France for the inspiration for Grande Couronne. The 26 year old single malt was initially matured in both American and European oak casks, before it was moved to French oak ex-Cognac casks for a lengthy two year finishing period. Something you don&#39;t see every day, it&#39;s brilliantly decadent stuff, presented in an appropriately embellished bottle and presentation box.</span></p>', 'Speyside\'s Glenfiddich Distillery looked to France for the inspiration for Grande Couronne.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 34, '', 'GLENFIDDICH 26 YEARS', 'Speyside\'s Glenfiddich Distillery looked to France for the inspiration for Grande Couronne.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Speyside&#39;s Glenfiddich Distillery looked to France for the inspiration for Grande Couronne. The 26 year old single malt was initially matured in both American and European oak casks, before it was moved to French oak ex-Cognac casks for a lengthy two year finishing period. Something you don&#39;t see every day, it&#39;s brilliantly decadent stuff, presented in an appropriately embellished bottle and presentation box.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000412', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 16:04:55', '2024-06-10 17:24:28'),
(413, '6656027590c84', 'PRO000413', 0, 'Glenmorangie Extra Matured Quinta Ruban 14 Years', '<div class=\"product-main__description rte d-pt20 mb20\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; font-family: Gotham, sans-serif; width: 603.896px;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">Dr Bill, our Director of Whisky Creation, was born with a taste for adventure. And with this single malt he sought to create a whisky as unpredictable as his travels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">The Quinta Ruban 14 Years Old is a whisky journey into the wild &ndash; a dark and delectable forest where the wind whistles with gusts of peppermint and dark swirls of chocolate can happen at any moment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">In our giraffe-high stills, it begins soft and fruity, then gets darker and deeper as we let it age for 14 years in bourbon casks and port casks from Portugal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">The finished whisky is a thicket of voluptuous flavour combinations. Walnut and black pepper. Mandarin orange and melted marshmallow. Dark chocolate bar and peppermint.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">Like stepping into a chocolate-minty-orange unknown, the journey is as delicious as the destination.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"accordion mt40 pb62\" data-accordion=\"product-page\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 40px; padding-bottom: 62px; color: rgb(33, 42, 47); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; border-top: none !important;\">&nbsp;</div>', 'The Quinta Ruban 14 Years Old is a whisky journey into the wild', 15, '', NULL, 35, 35, '', 'GLENMORANGIE EXTRA MATURED QUINTA RUBAN 14 YEARS', 'The Quinta Ruban 14 Years Old is a whisky journey into the wild', '<div class=\"product-main__description rte d-pt20 mb20\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; font-family: Gotham, sans-serif; width: 603.896px;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">Dr Bill, our Director of Whisky Creation, was born with a taste for adventure. And with this single malt he sought to create a whisky as unpredictable as his travels.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">The Quinta Ruban 14 Years Old is a whisky journey into the wild &ndash; a dark and delectable forest where the wind whistles with gusts of peppermint and dark swirls of chocolate can happen at any moment.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">In our giraffe-high stills, it begins soft and fruity, then gets darker and deeper as we let it age for 14 years in bourbon casks and port casks from Portugal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">The finished whisky is a thicket of voluptuous flavour combinations. Walnut and black pepper. Mandarin orange and melted marshmallow. Dark chocolate bar and peppermint.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: var(--body-spacing-1-d); font-style: var(--body-style-1); text-transform: var(--body-transform-1);\">Like stepping into a chocolate-minty-orange unknown, the journey is as delicious as the destination.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"accordion mt40 pb62\" data-accordion=\"product-page\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 40px; padding-bottom: 62px; color: rgb(33, 42, 47); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; border-top: none !important;\">&nbsp;</div>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000413', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 16:12:37', '2024-06-10 17:20:08'),
(414, '6656053a70fef', 'PRO000414', 0, 'Auchroisk 10 Years Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This single malt lies at the heart of the Auchroisk range, it being the only official bottling. Released in the Flora and Fauna series in 2001, having previously been marketed as The Singleton of Auchroisk.</span></p>', 'This single malt lies at the heart of the Auchroisk range, it being the only official bottling.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 152, '', 'AUCHROISK 10 YEARS SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'This single malt lies at the heart of the Auchroisk range, it being the only official bottling.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Roboto, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">This single malt lies at the heart of the Auchroisk range, it being the only official bottling. Released in the Flora and Fauna series in 2001, having previously been marketed as The Singleton of Auchroisk.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000414', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 16:24:26', '2024-06-10 17:16:03'),
(415, '665608a152c13', 'PRO000415', 0, 'Balblair 12 Years Highland Single Malt Whisky', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Balblair is what you imagine a distillery should be. Their&nbsp;home sits on an ancient Pictish gathering place, tucked away near the banks of the Dornoch Firth.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Their time-intensive methods make for more flavour-intensive malts. In the words of the&nbsp;Distillery Manager, John MacDonald, &ldquo;making whisky should be a craft, not a process.&rdquo; And he ensures this runs through every aspect of what they&nbsp;do, right down to how they&nbsp;label our casks. Ours are hand-stencilled and dated by the men who filled them, affording the&nbsp;whisky the respect it deserves.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In the fine balance of fruit, spice and sweetness, Balblair 12 Year Old encapsulates the gentle charisma of the Highlands. Elegant and approachable, this is the defining expression of Balblair Distillery, one to which all others refer.</p>', 'Balblair is what you imagine a distillery should be.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 153, '', 'BALBLAIR 12 YEARS HIGHLAND SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Balblair is what you imagine a distillery should be.', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Balblair is what you imagine a distillery should be. Their&nbsp;home sits on an ancient Pictish gathering place, tucked away near the banks of the Dornoch Firth.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Their time-intensive methods make for more flavour-intensive malts. In the words of the&nbsp;Distillery Manager, John MacDonald, &ldquo;making whisky should be a craft, not a process.&rdquo; And he ensures this runs through every aspect of what they&nbsp;do, right down to how they&nbsp;label our casks. Ours are hand-stencilled and dated by the men who filled them, affording the&nbsp;whisky the respect it deserves.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">In the fine balance of fruit, spice and sweetness, Balblair 12 Year Old encapsulates the gentle charisma of the Highlands. Elegant and approachable, this is the defining expression of Balblair Distillery, one to which all others refer.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000415', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 16:38:57', '2024-06-10 17:05:02'),
(416, '66560b8d47157', 'PRO000416', 0, 'The Balvenie 25 Years Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">The Balvenie Single Barrel Traditional Oak is&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(211, 227, 253) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 50%); background-position: 0% 0px; background-size: 200% 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(4, 12, 40); animation: 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.05, 0.7, 0.1, 1) 0.25s 1 normal forwards running highlight; font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">characterised by subtle spices and rich honeyed sweetness</span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">. Malt Master David C. Stewart MBE only selects casks of whisky for bottling that have the character he expects of Balvenie matured for 25 years exclusively in American oak.</span></p>', 'The Balvenie Single Barrel Traditional Oak is characterised by subtle spices and rich honeyed sweetness', 15, '', NULL, 35, 154, '', 'THE BALVENIE 25 YEARS SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'The Balvenie Single Barrel Traditional Oak is characterised by subtle spices and rich honeyed sweetness', '<p style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Lato, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">The Balvenie Single Barrel Traditional Oak is&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(211, 227, 253) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 50%); background-position: 0% 0px; background-size: 200% 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(4, 12, 40); animation: 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.05, 0.7, 0.1, 1) 0.25s 1 normal forwards running highlight; font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">characterised by subtle spices and rich honeyed sweetness</span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">. Malt Master David C. Stewart MBE only selects casks of whisky for bottling that have the character he expects of Balvenie matured for 25 years exclusively in American oak.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000416', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 16:51:25', '2024-06-10 17:01:31'),
(417, '66560e9229eeb', 'PRO000417', 0, 'Bowmore 10 Years Islay Single Malt Whisky 40%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 21, 22); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Dark &amp; Intense. Bowmore&rsquo;s 10 years old pushes the boundaries with bold flavour fusions. Spanish oak sherry casks develop spicy notes on our signature peat smoke in an intense marriage of fire and earth. Experience the layered spectrum of baked Seville orange, toasted maple, peat smoked walnuts and sherry.Dark &amp; Intense. Bowmore&rsquo;s 10 years old pushes the boundaries with bold flavour fusions. Spanish oak sherry casks develop spicy notes on our signature peat smoke in an intense marriage of fire and earth. Experience the layered spectrum of baked Seville orange, toasted maple, peat smoked walnuts and sherry.</span></p>', 'Dark & Intense. Bowmore’s 10 years old pushes the boundaries with bold flavour fusions.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 155, '', 'BOWMORE 10 YEARS ISLAY SINGLE MALT WHISKY 40%', 'Dark & Intense. Bowmore’s 10 years old pushes the boundaries with bold flavour fusions.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 21, 22); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Dark &amp; Intense. Bowmore&rsquo;s 10 years old pushes the boundaries with bold flavour fusions. Spanish oak sherry casks develop spicy notes on our signature peat smoke in an intense marriage of fire and earth. Experience the layered spectrum of baked Seville orange, toasted maple, peat smoked walnuts and sherry.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000417', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 17:04:18', '2024-06-10 17:00:55'),
(418, '665617bd0650b', 'PRO000418', 0, 'Bruichladdich Octomore 13.1 Edition Single Malt Whisky', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0.9375rem; margin-bottom: 0.9375rem; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Slate, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Nowhere is the dualism of their Octomore super heavily peated series more pertinent than in their .1 edition. Never as expected, delicate but powerful, this is unadulterated heavy smoke balanced with their vivacious and dynamic, fruity and floral distillate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0.9375rem; margin-bottom: 0.9375rem; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Slate, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">While Octomore in itself does not conform to tradition, their Head Distiller Adam Hannett is inclined to mature Octomore .1 editions solely in ex-American whiskey casks for 5 vibrant years. Octomore 13.1 is the necessary control for the rest of the series, as experiments within an experiment, but their baseline should not be underestimated. Mainland grown Scottish barley is distilled in a patient and considered trickle.</p>', 'Nowhere is the dualism of their Octomore super heavily peated series more pertinent than in their .1 edition.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 151, '', 'BRUICHLADDICH OCTOMORE 13.1 EDITION SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Nowhere is the dualism of their Octomore super heavily peated series more pertinent than in their .1 edition.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0.9375rem; margin-bottom: 0.9375rem; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Slate, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Nowhere is the dualism of their Octomore super heavily peated series more pertinent than in their .1 edition. Never as expected, delicate but powerful, this is unadulterated heavy smoke balanced with their vivacious and dynamic, fruity and floral distillate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: none; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin-top: 0.9375rem; margin-bottom: 0.9375rem; color: rgb(17, 17, 17); font-family: Slate, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">While Octomore in itself does not conform to tradition, their Head Distiller Adam Hannett is inclined to mature Octomore .1 editions solely in ex-American whiskey casks for 5 vibrant years. Octomore 13.1 is the necessary control for the rest of the series, as experiments within an experiment, but their baseline should not be underestimated. Mainland grown Scottish barley is distilled in a patient and considered trickle.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000418', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 17:43:25', '2024-06-10 16:50:02'),
(419, '665624c360ed3', 'PRO000419', 0, 'Glen Grant 10 Years Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.35px;\">First released in 2008, this single malt from the Glen Grant distillery in Speyside is matured for 10 years in ex-bourbon casks. Bottled at 43%. (Bottle size 750ml)</span></p>', 'First released in 2008, this single malt from the Glen Grant distillery in Speyside is matured for 10 years in ex-bourbon casks', 15, '', NULL, 35, 156, '', 'GLEN GRANT 10 YEARS SINLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'First released in 2008, this single malt from the Glen Grant distillery in Speyside is matured for 10 years in ex-bourbon casks', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 70, 70); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.35px;\">First released in 2008, this single malt from the Glen Grant distillery in Speyside is matured for 10 years in ex-bourbon casks. Bottled at 43%. (Bottle size 750ml)</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000419', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 18:38:59', '2024-06-10 16:43:44'),
(420, '665629412a8dc', 'PRO000420', 0, 'Glen Ord 13 Years 2008 Ucf Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(118, 118, 118); line-height: 1.84615; font-size: 0.928571rem; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">The Glen Ord Distillery</span></em>&nbsp;or also known as The Singleton of Glen Ord is a distillery in the Highland region of Scotland. It is the only remaining single malt producing distillery on the Black Isle. The distillery won awards in 1994 and 1996 for the best single malt at the International Wine &amp; Spirits Competition and also at the Monde Selection in 1996 and 1997. Boasting 7 wash stills and 7 spirits stills the output is a huge 11,500,00 litres of spirit each year used in Diageo blends mostly but also available as single malt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(118, 118, 118); line-height: 1.84615; font-size: 0.928571rem; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">This single malt whisky was distilled in&nbsp;2008 at&nbsp;the&nbsp;Glen Ord Distillery in the&nbsp;Highland region of&nbsp;Scotland. It was then&nbsp;placed into three separate&nbsp;Hogsheads for&nbsp;no less than&nbsp;13 years. Bottled with&nbsp;natural colour and no chill-filtration at 46% ABV&nbsp;from cask numbers 318697, 318698, 318700 as part of the Signatory Vintage&nbsp;Un-Cillfiltered&nbsp;Collection.</p>', 'The Glen Ord Distillery or also known as The Singleton of Glen Ord is a distillery in the Highland region of Scotland.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 157, '', 'GLEN ORD 13 YEARS 2008 UCF SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'The Glen Ord Distillery or also known as The Singleton of Glen Ord is a distillery in the Highland region of Scotland.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(118, 118, 118); line-height: 1.84615; font-size: 0.928571rem; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-weight: 700;\">The Glen Ord Distillery</span></em>&nbsp;or also known as The Singleton of Glen Ord is a distillery in the Highland region of Scotland. It is the only remaining single malt producing distillery on the Black Isle. The distillery won awards in 1994 and 1996 for the best single malt at the International Wine &amp; Spirits Competition and also at the Monde Selection in 1996 and 1997. Boasting 7 wash stills and 7 spirits stills the output is a huge 11,500,00 litres of spirit each year used in Diageo blends mostly but also available as single malt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(118, 118, 118); line-height: 1.84615; font-size: 0.928571rem; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">This single malt whisky was distilled in&nbsp;2008 at&nbsp;the&nbsp;Glen Ord Distillery in the&nbsp;Highland region of&nbsp;Scotland. It was then&nbsp;placed into three separate&nbsp;Hogsheads for&nbsp;no less than&nbsp;13 years. Bottled with&nbsp;natural colour and no chill-filtration at 46% ABV&nbsp;from cask numbers 318697, 318698, 318700 as part of the Signatory Vintage&nbsp;Un-Cillfiltered&nbsp;Collection.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000420', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 18:58:09', '2024-06-10 15:08:42'),
(421, '66562b2a4a6fc', 'PRO000421', 0, 'Glen Spey 12 Years Single Malt Whisky 43%', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 5px 0px 1.2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Indulge in the exquisite taste of Glen Spey 12 Years Old Single Malt Scotch Whisky. Crafted with precision and expertise, this premium whisky is a true delight for whisky enthusiasts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">With a volume of 700ml, this bottle of Glen Spey 12 Years Old offers an ample supply of this exceptional spirit. The 12 years of maturation have allowed the whisky to develop a rich and complex character that is sure to impress.</p>', 'Indulge in the exquisite taste of Glen Spey 12 Years Old Single Malt Scotch Whisky.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 158, '', 'GLEN SPEY 12 YEARS SINGLE MALT WHISKY 43%', 'Indulge in the exquisite taste of Glen Spey 12 Years Old Single Malt Scotch Whisky.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 5px 0px 1.2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Indulge in the exquisite taste of Glen Spey 12 Years Old Single Malt Scotch Whisky. Crafted with precision and expertise, this premium whisky is a true delight for whisky enthusiasts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">With a volume of 700ml, this bottle of Glen Spey 12 Years Old offers an ample supply of this exceptional spirit. The 12 years of maturation have allowed the whisky to develop a rich and complex character that is sure to impress.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000421', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 19:06:18', '2024-06-10 15:05:17'),
(422, '66562d212ae2d', 'PRO000422', 0, 'Glendronach Port Wood Highland Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 118, 118); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">GlenDronach distillery was founded in 1826 and is situated near Forgue, by Huntly, in Aberdeenshire, Scotland. It has had many owners&nbsp;through its long history but non as significant as when The BenRiach Distillery Company Ltd owned the distillery between 2008 and 2016. The owners made significant changes as to how the brand was positioned and marketed as well as&nbsp;changed the core range and undoubtedly placed this distillery on the map of sought after whisky.&nbsp;A significant amount of GlenDronach is now purchased for collection and investment. It has over the past decade slowly become the new Macallan of the Scottish whisky industry. Renowned for its signature style of whisky, matured in the finest Pedro Xim&egrave;nez and Oloroso Sherry casks.</span></p>', 'GlenDronach distillery was founded in 1826 and is situated near Forgue, by Huntly, in Aberdeenshire, Scotland.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 159, '', 'GLENDRONACH PORT WOOD HIGHLAND SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'GlenDronach distillery was founded in 1826 and is situated near Forgue, by Huntly, in Aberdeenshire, Scotland.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 118, 118); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;;\">GlenDronach distillery was founded in 1826 and is situated near Forgue, by Huntly, in Aberdeenshire, Scotland. It has had many owners&nbsp;through its long history but non as significant as when The BenRiach Distillery Company Ltd owned the distillery between 2008 and 2016. The owners made significant changes as to how the brand was positioned and marketed as well as&nbsp;changed the core range and undoubtedly placed this distillery on the map of sought after whisky.&nbsp;A significant amount of GlenDronach is now purchased for collection and investment. It has over the past decade slowly become the new Macallan of the Scottish whisky industry. Renowned for its signature style of whisky, matured in the finest Pedro Xim&egrave;nez and Oloroso Sherry casks.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000422', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 19:14:41', '2024-06-10 15:00:50'),
(423, '66562eba1760c', 'PRO000423', 0, 'Glengoyne 12 Years Single Malt Scotch Whisky 43%', '<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">The Glengoyne Time Keeper Gift Box is available online. Featuring a 70cl bottle of our zesty Glengoyne 12 Year Old, as well as a glass and tasting booklet in a beautiful festive box, it&rsquo;s sure to delight many whisky lovers as a gift.</p>\r\n\r\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">At Glengoyne, we savour time to create quality and know when to press pause in this fast-forward world. Like Time Keepers, we understand the merits of patience and precision, creating and treasuring memorable moments as a matter of course.</p>', 'The Glengoyne Time Keeper Gift Box is available online.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 150, '', 'GLENGOYNE 12 YEARS SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY 43%', 'The Glengoyne Time Keeper Gift Box is available online.', '<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">The Glengoyne Time Keeper Gift Box is available online. Featuring a 70cl bottle of our zesty Glengoyne 12 Year Old, as well as a glass and tasting booklet in a beautiful festive box, it&rsquo;s sure to delight many whisky lovers as a gift.</p>\r\n\r\n<p data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, &quot;Helvetica Neue Light&quot;, HelveticaNeue, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);\">At Glengoyne, we savour time to create quality and know when to press pause in this fast-forward world. Like Time Keepers, we understand the merits of patience and precision, creating and treasuring memorable moments as a matter of course.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000423', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 19:21:30', '2024-06-10 14:57:47'),
(424, '665632e56f7b8', 'PRO000424', 0, 'Speyburn 10 Years Highland Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Speyburn 10 Years Old is aged for at least 10 years in a combination of American ex-bourbon and ex-sherry casks.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Speyburn is a light, natural, sweet and classic Speyside whisky.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Speyside. Nothing more. Nothing less.</span></p>', 'Speyburn 10 Years Old is aged for at least 10 years in a combination of American ex-bourbon and ex-sherry casks.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 160, '', 'SPEYBURN 10 YEARS HIGHLAND SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'Speyburn 10 Years Old is aged for at least 10 years in a combination of American ex-bourbon and ex-sherry casks.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Speyburn 10 Years Old is aged for at least 10 years in a combination of American ex-bourbon and ex-sherry casks.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Speyburn is a light, natural, sweet and classic Speyside whisky.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(60, 60, 60); font-family: Urbanist, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Speyside. Nothing more. Nothing less.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000424', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-28 19:39:17', '2024-06-10 14:53:12'),
(425, '6656f37ed7980', 'PRO000425', 0, 'Glenfiddich 30 Years', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 6, 57); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Handcrafted by our expert Malt Master, Glenfiddich 30 Years Size: 700ML ABV: 43% SHERRY, FIG, DARK CHOCOLATE is an unparalleled expression aged in Spanish Oloroso and American bourbon oak for over 30 years. Each cask is carefully nosed, selected, and married to achieve a perfect blend of robust oak and sweet warmth. Discover the deep, complex flavors and masterful finish of this exceptional 30 Year Old.</span></p>', 'Handcrafted by our expert Malt Master, Glenfiddich 30 Years Size', 15, '', NULL, 35, 34, '', 'GLENFIDDICH 30 YEARS', 'Handcrafted by our expert Malt Master, Glenfiddich 30 Years Size', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 6, 57); font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Handcrafted by our expert Malt Master, Glenfiddich 30 Years Size: 700ML ABV: 43% SHERRY, FIG, DARK CHOCOLATE is an unparalleled expression aged in Spanish Oloroso and American bourbon oak for over 30 years. Each cask is carefully nosed, selected, and married to achieve a perfect blend of robust oak and sweet warmth. Discover the deep, complex flavors and masterful finish of this exceptional 30 Year Old.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000425', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 09:21:02', '2024-06-10 14:50:31'),
(426, '6656f4f17c7c4', 'PRO000426', 0, 'Glenfiddich 12 Years', '<p><span class=\"styled__Block-mfe-pdp__sc-1od89q4-1 bICtby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; white-space-collapse: preserve-breaks; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;TESCO Modern&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Flowing in the Valley of the Deer since 1887, our family&#39;s signature expression is the world&#39;s most awarded single malt Scotch whisky.</span><span class=\"styled__Block-mfe-pdp__sc-1od89q4-1 bICtby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; white-space-collapse: preserve-breaks; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;TESCO Modern&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">With a unique freshness from the same Highland spring water we&#39;ve used since 1887, its distinctive fruitiness comes from the high cut point William Grant always insisted upon. Carefully matured in the finest American oak and European oak sherry casks for at least 12 years, it is mellowed in oak marrying tuns to create its sweet and subtle oak flavours.</span></p>', 'Flowing in the Valley of the Deer since 1887, our family\'s signature expression is the world\'s most awarded single malt', 15, '', NULL, 35, 34, '', 'GLENFIDDICH 12 YEARS', 'Flowing in the Valley of the Deer since 1887, our family\'s signature expression is the world\'s most awarded single malt', '<p><span class=\"styled__Block-mfe-pdp__sc-1od89q4-1 bICtby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; white-space-collapse: preserve-breaks; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;TESCO Modern&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Flowing in the Valley of the Deer since 1887, our family&#39;s signature expression is the world&#39;s most awarded single malt Scotch whisky.</span><span class=\"styled__Block-mfe-pdp__sc-1od89q4-1 bICtby\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; display: block; white-space-collapse: preserve-breaks; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;TESCO Modern&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">With a unique freshness from the same Highland spring water we&#39;ve used since 1887, its distinctive fruitiness comes from the high cut point William Grant always insisted upon. Carefully matured in the finest American oak and European oak sherry casks for at least 12 years, it is mellowed in oak marrying tuns to create its sweet and subtle oak flavours.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000426', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 09:27:13', '2024-06-10 14:46:01'),
(427, '6656f627bdb31', 'PRO000427', 0, 'Glenfiddich 18 Years', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">An elegant nose, faintly sweet, scented with apple and wood. Glenfiddich 18yo is a robust and full-bodied single malt whisky, yet remains remarkably soft, rounded and long lasting.</span></p>', 'An elegant nose, faintly sweet, scented with apple and wood.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 34, '', 'GLENFIDDICH 18 YEARS', 'An elegant nose, faintly sweet, scented with apple and wood.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: lato, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.32px;\">An elegant nose, faintly sweet, scented with apple and wood. Glenfiddich 18yo is a robust and full-bodied single malt whisky, yet remains remarkably soft, rounded and long lasting.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000427', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 09:32:23', '2024-06-10 14:43:36'),
(428, '6656f795c7543', 'PRO000428', 0, 'Rampur Single Malt Asava 45%', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 21, 1); font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Matured in American Bourbon barrels and meticulously perfected in Indian Cabernet Sauvignon casks for the first time in History resulting in a unique expression with and impeccable balance.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 21, 1); font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Tasting Notes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 21, 1); font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Nose: Typical tropical fruity note of Rampur with added notes of apricot, blackberry &amp; plum followed with a faint hint of tobacco and spices.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 21, 1); font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Palate: Velvety, manuka honey sweetness highlighted by spicy oak, vanilla and balanced with dryness from Indian red wine.</p>', 'Matured in American Bourbon barrels and meticulously perfected in Indian Cabernet Sauvignon casks', 15, '', NULL, 35, 161, '', 'RAMPUR SINGLE MALT ASAVA 45%', 'Matured in American Bourbon barrels and meticulously perfected in Indian Cabernet Sauvignon casks', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 21, 1); font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Matured in American Bourbon barrels and meticulously perfected in Indian Cabernet Sauvignon casks for the first time in History resulting in a unique expression with and impeccable balance.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 21, 1); font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Tasting Notes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 21, 1); font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Nose: Typical tropical fruity note of Rampur with added notes of apricot, blackberry &amp; plum followed with a faint hint of tobacco and spices.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem; padding: 0px; color: rgb(45, 21, 1); font-family: &quot;Josefin Sans&quot;, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Palate: Velvety, manuka honey sweetness highlighted by spicy oak, vanilla and balanced with dryness from Indian red wine.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000428', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 09:38:29', '2024-06-10 14:38:33'),
(429, '6656f92889392', 'PRO000429', 0, 'Laphroaig Islay Single Malt Scotch Whisky Quarter Cask', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Laphroaig Quarter Cask Single Malt Islay Peated Whisky is a bold expression that&rsquo;s double matured in two barrels made of American oak</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Taking inspiration from the old tradition of transporting whisky on packhorses, smaller quarter-sized casks are used to amplify the peaty smokiness along with a surprising sweetness imparting warm and spicy oak flavors</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Laphroaig Quarter Cask Single Malt Islay Peated Whisky is a bold expression', 15, '', NULL, 35, 162, '', 'LAPHROAIG ISLAY SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY QUARTER CASK', 'Laphroaig Quarter Cask Single Malt Islay Peated Whisky is a bold expression', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 17); padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">\r\n	<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Laphroaig Quarter Cask Single Malt Islay Peated Whisky is a bold expression that&rsquo;s double matured in two barrels made of American oak</span></li>\r\n	<li class=\"a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Taking inspiration from the old tradition of transporting whisky on packhorses, smaller quarter-sized casks are used to amplify the peaty smokiness along with a surprising sweetness imparting warm and spicy oak flavors</span></li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000429', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 09:45:12', '2024-06-10 14:32:40'),
(430, '6656fb3fb1b5b', 'PRO000430', 0, 'Dalmore 15 Years Highland Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 29, 27); font-family: cerapro, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.375px; text-align: center;\">Each hand selected sherry cask gifts the Dalmore 15 with its own individual characteristics and flavors, to compliment the base notes of soft vanilla and honey from the American white oak ex-bourbon barrels.</span></p>', 'Each hand selected sherry cask gifts the Dalmore 15 with its own individual characteristics and flavors', 15, '', NULL, 35, 163, '', 'DALMORE 15 YEARS HIGHLAND SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'Each hand selected sherry cask gifts the Dalmore 15 with its own individual characteristics and flavors', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 29, 27); font-family: cerapro, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: -0.375px; text-align: center;\">Each hand selected sherry cask gifts the Dalmore 15 with its own individual characteristics and flavors, to compliment the base notes of soft vanilla and honey from the American white oak ex-bourbon barrels.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000430', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 09:54:07', '2024-06-10 14:26:18');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `uniqid`, `product_item_id`, `supplier_id`, `product_name`, `description`, `short_description`, `category_id`, `product_image`, `images`, `subcategory_id`, `brand_id`, `video`, `product_name_fr`, `short_description_fr`, `page_content_fr`, `product_qty`, `tech_data_sheet`, `retail_price`, `discount_price`, `is_admin_approve`, `most_view`, `is_product_bestseller`, `sku`, `average_rating`, `offer`, `status`, `in_store`, `in_online`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(431, '665701452a5b2', 'PRO000431', 0, 'The Glenlivet Founder Reserve With 2 Glass', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 50, 37); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Boasting the classic flavours of The Glenlivet bound up in a creamy, smooth texture, The Glenlivet Founder&#39;s Reserve single malt whisky is our tribute to the man who started it all. When George Smith began distilling, The Glenlivet had no age statements and he selected whisky from casks of a range of ages.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 50, 37); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Made with water from the same crystal-clear mountain streams, in the same cold, pure air, The Glenlivet Founder?s Reserve is as smooth and fruity as the whisky that first ran from the original copper pot stills.</span></p>', 'Boasting the classic flavours of The Glenlivet bound up in a creamy, smooth texture.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 164, '', 'THE GLENLIVET FOUNDER RESERVE WITH 2 GLASS', 'Boasting the classic flavours of The Glenlivet bound up in a creamy, smooth texture.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 50, 37); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Boasting the classic flavours of The Glenlivet bound up in a creamy, smooth texture, The Glenlivet Founder&#39;s Reserve single malt whisky is our tribute to the man who started it all. When George Smith began distilling, The Glenlivet had no age statements and he selected whisky from casks of a range of ages.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 50, 37); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">Made with water from the same crystal-clear mountain streams, in the same cold, pure air, The Glenlivet Founder?s Reserve is as smooth and fruity as the whisky that first ran from the original copper pot stills.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000431', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 10:19:49', '2024-06-10 14:20:22'),
(432, '665703620581e', 'PRO000432', 0, 'Jura 21 Years Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.425px; line-height: var(--typeBaseLineHeight); font-size: 17px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29);\">In the vast wilderness of our island home, it&rsquo;s easy to lose track of time. But if you stop a moment in that beautiful wilderness and take in the silence, eventually you&rsquo;ll notice the rhythm of the tide bringing you back. Like the whisky in our casks, it&rsquo;s an irresistible reminder of time&rsquo;s power.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.425px; line-height: var(--typeBaseLineHeight); font-size: 17px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29);\">Matured in American white oak ex bourbon barrels, this whisky is then finished in hand-selected virgin American white oak casks, giving it a sweet, fruity and nutty flavour. This truly special whisky is available worldwide.</p>', 'In the vast wilderness of our island home, it’s easy to lose track of time.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 165, '', 'JURA 21 YEARS SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'In the vast wilderness of our island home, it’s easy to lose track of time.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.425px; line-height: var(--typeBaseLineHeight); font-size: 17px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29);\">In the vast wilderness of our island home, it&rsquo;s easy to lose track of time. But if you stop a moment in that beautiful wilderness and take in the silence, eventually you&rsquo;ll notice the rhythm of the tide bringing you back. Like the whisky in our casks, it&rsquo;s an irresistible reminder of time&rsquo;s power.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.425px; line-height: var(--typeBaseLineHeight); font-size: 17px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px; color: rgb(28, 29, 29);\">Matured in American white oak ex bourbon barrels, this whisky is then finished in hand-selected virgin American white oak casks, giving it a sweet, fruity and nutty flavour. This truly special whisky is available worldwide.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000432', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 10:28:50', '2024-06-10 14:14:18'),
(433, '66570d551ae3e', 'PRO000433', 0, 'Dalmore Cigar Malt', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;\">Dalmore, located on the northern shores of the Firth of Cromarty, deep in the Scottish Highlands has been making single malt whiskies since 1839 and the bottles still bear the stag crest of the Clan Mackenzie. Their Cigar Malt Reserve is a wonderful blend of three different oak types of 10-15-year-old whiskies. White American oak, 30-year-old Matusalem Olorosso Sherry casks and Premier Cru Cabernet Sauvignon wine barriques. The final blend has an enveloping aroma and flavour of the finest hand-made cigars; rich and smoky and extremely long-lasting.</span></p>', 'Dalmore, located on the northern shores of the Firth of Cromarty', 15, '', NULL, 35, 163, '', 'DALMORE CIGAR MALT', 'Dalmore, located on the northern shores of the Firth of Cromarty', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Futura, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.4px;\">Dalmore, located on the northern shores of the Firth of Cromarty, deep in the Scottish Highlands has been making single malt whiskies since 1839 and the bottles still bear the stag crest of the Clan Mackenzie. Their Cigar Malt Reserve is a wonderful blend of three different oak types of 10-15-year-old whiskies. White American oak, 30-year-old Matusalem Olorosso Sherry casks and Premier Cru Cabernet Sauvignon wine barriques. The final blend has an enveloping aroma and flavour of the finest hand-made cigars; rich and smoky and extremely long-lasting.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000433', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:11:17', '2024-06-10 14:08:32'),
(434, '66570f9e4d1bf', 'PRO000434', 0, 'Glenmorangie The Nectar D\'or', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">Glenmore Nectar d&#39;or is&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(211, 227, 253) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 50%); background-position: 0% 0px; background-size: 200% 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(4, 12, 40); animation: 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.05, 0.7, 0.1, 1) 0.25s 1 normal forwards running highlight; font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">a unique Scotch Whisky extra matured in rare Sauternes wine barriques from France</span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">, creating a silky and sumptuous single malt with layers of lemon, white chocolate and honey.</span></p>', 'Glenmore Nectar d\'or is a unique Scotch Whisky extra matured in rare Sauternes wine', 15, '', NULL, 35, 35, '', 'GLENMORANGIE THE NECTAR D\'OR', 'Glenmore Nectar d\'or is a unique Scotch Whisky extra matured in rare Sauternes wine', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">Glenmore Nectar d&#39;or is&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(211, 227, 253) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 50%); background-position: 0% 0px; background-size: 200% 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(4, 12, 40); animation: 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.05, 0.7, 0.1, 1) 0.25s 1 normal forwards running highlight; font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">a unique Scotch Whisky extra matured in rare Sauternes wine barriques from France</span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">, creating a silky and sumptuous single malt with layers of lemon, white chocolate and honey.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000434', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:21:02', '2024-06-10 14:05:50'),
(435, '6657103b52d05', 'PRO000435', 0, 'Glenmorangie The Lasanta 12 Years', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Creators of Highland Single Malt Scotch Whiskies since 1843. Elegant but full bodied this whisky has spent ten years maturing in American white oak ex-bourbon casks before being extra-matured for a further two years in Oloroso and PX Sherry casks from Jerez in Spain. Lasanta is Gaelic for warmth and passion, a reminder not just of the Spanish provenance of these Oloros</span></p>', 'Creators of Highland Single Malt Scotch Whiskies since 1843.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 35, '', 'GLENMORANGIE THE LASANTA 12 YEARS', 'Creators of Highland Single Malt Scotch Whiskies since 1843.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Creators of Highland Single Malt Scotch Whiskies since 1843. Elegant but full bodied this whisky has spent ten years maturing in American white oak ex-bourbon casks before being extra-matured for a further two years in Oloroso and PX Sherry casks from Jerez in Spain. Lasanta is Gaelic for warmth and passion, a reminder not just of the Spanish provenance of these Oloros</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000435', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:23:39', '2024-06-10 13:56:25'),
(436, '665710de06c43', 'PRO000436', 0, 'Brenne French Single Malt Whiskey', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Launched in 2012 by Allison Parc, collaborating with a French distiller in Cognac, Brenne French Single Malt Whisky is something quite special indeed. It&#39;s made with malted barley grown in Cognac, double distilled, then initially matured in Limousin oak casks before enjoying a finishing period in Cognac casks. Each bottle is drawn from a single cask and is bottled at 40% ABV. Rather cool stuff indeed.</span></p>', 'Launched in 2012 by Allison Parc, collaborating with a French distiller in Cognac,', 15, '', NULL, 35, 166, '', 'BRENNE FRENCH SINGLE MALT WHISKEY', 'Launched in 2012 by Allison Parc, collaborating with a French distiller in Cognac,', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(75, 75, 75); font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Launched in 2012 by Allison Parc, collaborating with a French distiller in Cognac, Brenne French Single Malt Whisky is something quite special indeed. It&#39;s made with malted barley grown in Cognac, double distilled, then initially matured in Limousin oak casks before enjoying a finishing period in Cognac casks. Each bottle is drawn from a single cask and is bottled at 40% ABV. Rather cool stuff indeed.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000436', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:26:22', '2024-06-10 13:51:47'),
(437, '665711fc4e58f', 'PRO000437', 0, 'The Macallan Rare Cask 43%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.07px;\">The Macallan Rare Cask single malt Scotch whisky was introduced to the UK in mid 2015, after being launched in the US in late 2014. It&rsquo;s comprised of whiskies drawn from 16 different Sherry cask styles, chosen by Macallan&rsquo;s Master Whisky Maker Bob Dalgarno. A high proportion of these casks are first fill, and has resulted in a rich, spicy Speyside single malt, bursting with honey&rsquo;d raisin, root ginger and decadent chocolate notes. &nbsp; Nose:&nbsp;Rich Sherried spices, with a good helping of chocolate-coated raisins and Sherry-dipped plums. A refreshing burst of honeydew melon develops with a drop of water.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'The Macallan Rare Cask single malt Scotch whisky was introduced to the UK in mid 2015', 15, '', NULL, 35, 167, '', 'THE MACALLAN RARE CASK 43%', 'The Macallan Rare Cask single malt Scotch whisky was introduced to the UK in mid 2015', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.07px;\">The Macallan Rare Cask single malt Scotch whisky was introduced to the UK in mid 2015, after being launched in the US in late 2014. It&rsquo;s comprised of whiskies drawn from 16 different Sherry cask styles, chosen by Macallan&rsquo;s Master Whisky Maker Bob Dalgarno. A high proportion of these casks are first fill, and has resulted in a rich, spicy Speyside single malt, bursting with honey&rsquo;d raisin, root ginger and decadent chocolate notes. &nbsp; Nose:&nbsp;Rich Sherried spices, with a good helping of chocolate-coated raisins and Sherry-dipped plums. A refreshing burst of honeydew melon develops with a drop of water.&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000437', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:31:08', '2024-06-10 13:39:34'),
(438, '66571318e6da9', 'PRO000438', 0, 'Glenmorangie Signet', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Signet begins with our precious chocolate malt spirit, made just once a year in our giraffe-high stills. Its espresso-like intensity fills our Distillery with aromas more familiar in an Italian coffee bar.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Over the years, we temper its power with rare and treasured casks. Bourbon for creaminess. Sherry for sweetness. The spice of virgin charred oak. All balanced by some of the oldest whisky we own.</span></p>', 'Signet begins with our precious chocolate malt spirit', 15, '', NULL, 35, 35, '', 'GLENMORANGIE SIGNET 700 ML', 'Signet begins with our precious chocolate malt spirit', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Signet begins with our precious chocolate malt spirit, made just once a year in our giraffe-high stills. Its espresso-like intensity fills our Distillery with aromas more familiar in an Italian coffee bar.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 17px; line-height: 25.5px; letter-spacing: -0.34px; font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;\"><span data-mce-fragment=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Over the years, we temper its power with rare and treasured casks. Bourbon for creaminess. Sherry for sweetness. The spice of virgin charred oak. All balanced by some of the oldest whisky we own.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000438', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:35:52', '2024-06-10 13:37:13'),
(439, '665713ee67a59', 'PRO000439', 0, 'The Macallan A Night On Earth 40%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 28, 25); font-family: din-2014, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.1782px;\">Telling the story of Scotland&rsquo;s world-famous Hogmanay festivities celebrated annually on 31st December, A Night on Earth in Scotland captures the universal joy of celebrating the change of year. Nose: Vanilla, butter rich, baked apple, baking biscuits, plum and almond. Palate: Soft velvety sweetness reminiscent of shortbread with a rich mouth coating, vanilla sweetness, with lightly toasted marshmallow, dried oranges, fig and cinnamon. Finish: Medium finish with sweet butterscotch and freshly baked biscuits.</span></p>', 'Telling the story of Scotland’s world-famous Hogmanay festivities celebrated annually on 31st December', 15, '', NULL, 35, 167, '', 'THE MACALLAN A NIGHT ON EARTH 40%', 'Telling the story of Scotland’s world-famous Hogmanay festivities celebrated annually on 31st December', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 28, 25); font-family: din-2014, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.1782px;\">Telling the story of Scotland&rsquo;s world-famous Hogmanay festivities celebrated annually on 31st December, A Night on Earth in Scotland captures the universal joy of celebrating the change of year. Nose: Vanilla, butter rich, baked apple, baking biscuits, plum and almond. Palate: Soft velvety sweetness reminiscent of shortbread with a rich mouth coating, vanilla sweetness, with lightly toasted marshmallow, dried oranges, fig and cinnamon. Finish: Medium finish with sweet butterscotch and freshly baked biscuits.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000439', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:39:26', '2024-06-10 13:31:35'),
(440, '6657149212ca7', 'PRO000440', 0, 'The Macallan The Harmony Collection 44%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; word-spacing: 0.016px;\">This special single malt is inspired by the Ethiopian Arabica bean. Ethiopia is claimed to be the birthplace of coffee as the Arabica bean was the first species of coffee to be cultivated. With a distinct coffee flavour, this whisky exudes notes of espresso, dark chocolate and sweet oak. The intensely flavoured single malt invites you to immerse yourself in a sensory journey through flavour and aroma.</span></p>', 'This special single malt is inspired by the Ethiopian Arabica bean.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 167, '', 'THE MACALLAN THE HARMONY COLLECTION 44%', 'This special single malt is inspired by the Ethiopian Arabica bean.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 78, 78); font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;; font-size: 16px; word-spacing: 0.016px;\">This special single malt is inspired by the Ethiopian Arabica bean. Ethiopia is claimed to be the birthplace of coffee as the Arabica bean was the first species of coffee to be cultivated. With a distinct coffee flavour, this whisky exudes notes of espresso, dark chocolate and sweet oak. The intensely flavoured single malt invites you to immerse yourself in a sensory journey through flavour and aroma.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000440', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:42:10', '2024-06-10 13:21:13'),
(441, '6657157ccc22c', 'PRO000441', 0, 'The Macallan M Mmxx 2020 Release', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 65, 81); font-family: __frankNew_4e2c8c, __frankNew_Fallback_4e2c8c; font-size: 16px;\">Part of The Macallan M Collection Series created to showcase the beautiful range of The Macallan&rsquo;s Natural Colour, M is born of a collaboration between three masters of their crafts to create a completely individual spirit.Part of The Macallan M Collection Series created to showcase the beautiful range of The Macallan&rsquo;s Natural Colour, M is born of a collaboration between three masters of their crafts to create a completely individual spirit.</span></p>', 'Part of The Macallan M Collection Series created to showcase the beautiful range of The Macallan', 15, '', NULL, 35, 167, '', 'THE MACALLAN M MMXX 2020 RELEASE', 'Part of The Macallan M Collection Series created to showcase the beautiful range of The Macallan', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(55, 65, 81); font-family: __frankNew_4e2c8c, __frankNew_Fallback_4e2c8c; font-size: 16px;\">Part of The Macallan M Collection Series created to showcase the beautiful range of The Macallan&rsquo;s Natural Colour, M is born of a collaboration between three masters of their crafts to create a completely individual spirit.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000441', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:46:04', '2024-06-10 13:07:07'),
(442, '66571766a44ca', 'PRO000442', 0, 'Speymhor 21 Single Malt Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 27, 27); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The 21 Year Old Speymhor Single Malt was distilled in the Speyside region, which is the region that hosts the most Malt Whisky distilleries in Scotland. The world renowned River Spey brings copious quantities of fresh, clean water to the local distilleries which together with the mountain air and rural nature of Speyside combine to produce the magical quality of Speyside Malts. This Malt has been aged in former bourbon casks which have enhanced its development.</span></p>', 'The 21 Year Old Speymhor Single Malt was distilled in the Speyside region', 15, '', NULL, 35, 168, '', 'SPEYMHOR 21 SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY', 'The 21 Year Old Speymhor Single Malt was distilled in the Speyside region', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(28, 27, 27); font-family: &quot;Nunito Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250);\">The 21 Year Old Speymhor Single Malt was distilled in the Speyside region, which is the region that hosts the most Malt Whisky distilleries in Scotland. The world renowned River Spey brings copious quantities of fresh, clean water to the local distilleries which together with the mountain air and rural nature of Speyside combine to produce the magical quality of Speyside Malts. This Malt has been aged in former bourbon casks which have enhanced its development.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000442', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:54:14', '2024-06-10 13:02:25'),
(443, '665718531fdc6', 'PRO000443', 0, 'Talisker 10 Years 45.8%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Antenna-regular; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.6px;\">A fragrant and fresh nose. Sweet pear and apple peels come through thick, aromatic smoke, with pinches of maritime salt from kippers and seaweed. It&rsquo;s a peat bonfire with black pepper, a hint of brine, and dried barley. A gorgeous and delicate balance is provided by the pleasant arrival of orchard fruit. Bonfire embers roast malt and crystallize a sweet underlay in the lengthy aftertaste.</span></p>', 'A fragrant and fresh nose. Sweet pear and apple peels come through thick, aromatic smoke', 15, '', NULL, 35, 169, '', 'TALISKER 10 YEARS 45.8%', 'A fragrant and fresh nose. Sweet pear and apple peels come through thick, aromatic smoke', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Antenna-regular; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.6px;\">A fragrant and fresh nose. Sweet pear and apple peels come through thick, aromatic smoke, with pinches of maritime salt from kippers and seaweed. It&rsquo;s a peat bonfire with black pepper, a hint of brine, and dried barley. A gorgeous and delicate balance is provided by the pleasant arrival of orchard fruit. Bonfire embers roast malt and crystallize a sweet underlay in the lengthy aftertaste.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000443', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 11:58:11', '2024-06-10 12:55:04'),
(444, '665719bb0479f', 'PRO000444', 0, 'Tobermory 12 Single Malt Scotch Whisky 46.3%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(53, 53, 53, 0.75); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.6px;\">Bottled at 46.3% abv, with natural colour and non chill-filtered, the Tobermory 12 year old is the signature expression in the Tobermory core range. Sweet orange and citrus, creamy caramel and rich vanilla with spicy hints of cinnamon and clove.</span></p>', 'Bottled at 46.3% abv, with natural colour and non chill-filtered', 15, '', NULL, 35, 170, '', 'TOBERMORY 12 SINGLE MALT SCOTCH WHISKY 46.3%', 'Bottled at 46.3% abv, with natural colour and non chill-filtered', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(53, 53, 53, 0.75); font-family: Inter, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.6px;\">Bottled at 46.3% abv, with natural colour and non chill-filtered, the Tobermory 12 year old is the signature expression in the Tobermory core range. Sweet orange and citrus, creamy caramel and rich vanilla with spicy hints of cinnamon and clove.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000444', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 12:04:11', '2024-06-10 12:51:40'),
(445, '66571b103e62b', 'PRO000445', 0, 'Loch Lomond 12 Years Single Malt Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Loch Lomond 12 year old is a perfect representation of our signature style, delivering delicious notes of peach and pear, layered with vanilla sweetness and a gentle hint of smoke on the finish.</span></p>', 'Loch Lomond 12 year old is a perfect representation of our signature style', 15, '', NULL, 35, 171, '', 'LOCH LOMOND 12 YEARS SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Loch Lomond 12 year old is a perfect representation of our signature style', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Loch Lomond 12 year old is a perfect representation of our signature style, delivering delicious notes of peach and pear, layered with vanilla sweetness and a gentle hint of smoke on the finish.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000445', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 12:09:52', '2024-06-10 12:42:43'),
(446, '66571cc191e10', 'PRO000446', 0, 'Loch Lomond Original Single Malt Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Loch Lomond Original is an exceptionally smooth, full-bodied and easy drinking single malt scotch whisky. Matured in our finest oak casks, this whisky delivers&nbsp;a&nbsp;burst of sweet honey &amp; citrus notes with a gentle hint of smoke on the finish.</span></p>', 'Loch Lomond Original is an exceptionally smooth, full-bodied and easy drinking single malt scotch whisky.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 171, '', 'LOCH LOMOND ORIGINAL SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Loch Lomond Original is an exceptionally smooth, full-bodied and easy drinking single malt scotch whisky.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Loch Lomond Original is an exceptionally smooth, full-bodied and easy drinking single malt scotch whisky. Matured in our finest oak casks, this whisky delivers&nbsp;a&nbsp;burst of sweet honey &amp; citrus notes with a gentle hint of smoke on the finish.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000446', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 12:17:05', '2024-06-10 12:37:43'),
(447, '66571d89edf60', 'PRO000447', 0, 'Loch Lomond 12 Years Inchmurrin Single Malt Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Aged in three types of American Oak casks,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.lochlomondwhiskies.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(163, 128, 79); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Loch Lomond</a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;Inchmurrin 12 year old single malt shows off the fruit and sweet elements of our distillery&#39;s signature style with delightful notes of peach, apricot, toffee and vanilla.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Aged in three types of American Oak casks, Loch Lomond Inchmurrin 12 year old', 15, '', NULL, 35, 171, '', 'LOCH LOMOND 12 YEARS INCHMURRIN SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Aged in three types of American Oak casks, Loch Lomond Inchmurrin 12 year old', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Aged in three types of American Oak casks,&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.lochlomondwhiskies.com/\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(163, 128, 79); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; transition: color 0.3s ease-in-out 0s; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Loch Lomond</a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;Inchmurrin 12 year old single malt shows off the fruit and sweet elements of our distillery&#39;s signature style with delightful notes of peach, apricot, toffee and vanilla.&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000447', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 12:20:25', '2024-06-10 12:34:28'),
(448, '66571e6e478b1', 'PRO000448', 0, 'Loch Lomond 12 Years Inchmoan Single Malt Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Loch Lomond Inchmoan 12 year old is matured for 12 years in refill and rechar casks ensuring the sweeter notes of this single malt are brought to the fore. The result is a perfectly balanced combination of sweet vanilla, soft peat smoke and spice.</span></p>', 'Loch Lomond Inchmoan 12 year old is matured for 12 years', 15, '', NULL, 35, 171, '', 'LOCH LOMOND 12 YEARS INCHMOAN SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Loch Lomond Inchmoan 12 year old is matured for 12 years', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Loch Lomond Inchmoan 12 year old is matured for 12 years in refill and rechar casks ensuring the sweeter notes of this single malt are brought to the fore. The result is a perfectly balanced combination of sweet vanilla, soft peat smoke and spice.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000448', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 12:24:14', '2024-06-10 12:30:30'),
(449, '665720211cd80', 'PRO000449', 0, 'Glen Scotia Harbour Single Malt Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Campbeltown&#39;s iconic harbour was once the last stop for Scotch whisky of all regions to the wider world, and our aptly named &quot;Campbeltown Harbour&quot; is a toast to this important port, and the long-standing relationships it has forged between Campbeltown and the wider world.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Glen Scotia&nbsp;Campbeltown Harbour whisky is a superb introduction to the Glen Scotia range, with a distinct coastal influence of sea salt &amp; gentle smoke, balanced with soft peach and vanilla custard.</span></p>', 'Campbeltown\'s iconic harbour was once the last stop for Scotch whisky of all regions to the wider world', 15, '', NULL, 35, 172, '', 'GLEN SCOTIA HARBOUR SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Campbeltown\'s iconic harbour was once the last stop for Scotch whisky of all regions to the wider world', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Campbeltown&#39;s iconic harbour was once the last stop for Scotch whisky of all regions to the wider world, and our aptly named &quot;Campbeltown Harbour&quot; is a toast to this important port, and the long-standing relationships it has forged between Campbeltown and the wider world.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Glen Scotia&nbsp;Campbeltown Harbour whisky is a superb introduction to the Glen Scotia range, with a distinct coastal influence of sea salt &amp; gentle smoke, balanced with soft peach and vanilla custard.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000449', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 12:31:29', '2024-06-10 12:15:16'),
(450, '665730972ec82', 'PRO000450', 0, 'Glen Scotia Double Cask Single Malt Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Glen Scotia Double Cask whisky is a superb introduction to the Glen Scotia range for whisky explorers. With tastes of toffee and fudge, it&rsquo;s a perfect demonstration that at Glen Scotia, age is no indication of character.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Matured in first fill bourbon barrels before being finished for 12 months in PX sherry casks, this expression provides an intriguing harmony or rich and spicy fruit flavours, as well as distinctly Campbeltown notes.Glen Scotia Double Cask whisky is a superb introduction to the Glen Scotia range for whisky explorers. With tastes of toffee and fudge, it&rsquo;s a perfect demonstration that at Glen Scotia, age is no indication of character.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', 'Glen Scotia Double Cask whisky is a superb introduction to the Glen Scotia range for whisky explorers.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 172, '', 'GLEN SCOTIA DOUBLE CASK SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Glen Scotia Double Cask whisky is a superb introduction to the Glen Scotia range for whisky explorers.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Glen Scotia Double Cask whisky is a superb introduction to the Glen Scotia range for whisky explorers. With tastes of toffee and fudge, it&rsquo;s a perfect demonstration that at Glen Scotia, age is no indication of character.</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\" />\r\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trade Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Matured in first fill bourbon barrels before being finished for 12 months in PX sherry casks, this expression provides an intriguing harmony or rich and spicy fruit flavours, as well as distinctly Campbeltown notes.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000450', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 13:41:43', '2024-06-10 12:09:27'),
(451, '665732ee40aa7', 'PRO000451', 0, 'Bushmills 10 Years Single Malt Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: titling-gothic-fb, serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Bushmills 10 year old single malt whiskey is triple distilled from 100% malted barley and matured for at least 10 years in sherry and bourbon seasoned barrels, which give it honey, vanilla and milk chocolate flavours and is best served neat or over ice. We call it the perfect &ldquo;summertime whiskey,&rdquo; when poured over two ice cubes.</span></p>', 'Bushmills 10 year old single malt whiskey is triple distilled from 100% malted barley', 15, '', NULL, 35, 173, '', 'BUSHMILLS 10 YRS SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Bushmills 10 year old single malt whiskey is triple distilled from 100% malted barley', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: titling-gothic-fb, serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Bushmills 10 year old single malt whiskey is triple distilled from 100% malted barley and matured for at least 10 years in sherry and bourbon seasoned barrels, which give it honey, vanilla and milk chocolate flavours and is best served neat or over ice. We call it the perfect &ldquo;summertime whiskey,&rdquo; when poured over two ice cubes.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000451', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 13:51:42', '2024-06-10 12:03:00'),
(452, '665734a38688b', 'PRO000452', 0, 'Glenmorangie 18 Years', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Founded in 1843 in the Royal Burgh of Tain, in the far north of Scotland, Glenmorangie is Scotland&#39;s Favourite Single Malt Scotch Whisky. The distillery is famous for its distinctive tall stills - the tallest in Scotland - which play an important role in the development of the complex and fruity house style. We are also recognised as the pioneer of extra-maturation in the 1980s and for innovative work in the field of cask management since the early 1990s.&nbsp;</span></p>', 'The distillery is famous for its distinctive tall stills - the tallest in Scotland', 15, '', NULL, 35, 35, '', 'GLENMORANGIE 18 YEARS', 'The distillery is famous for its distinctive tall stills - the tallest in Scotland', '<p><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Amazon Ember&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Founded in 1843 in the Royal Burgh of Tain, in the far north of Scotland, Glenmorangie is Scotland&#39;s Favourite Single Malt Scotch Whisky. The distillery is famous for its distinctive tall stills - the tallest in Scotland - which play an important role in the development of the complex and fruity house style. We are also recognised as the pioneer of extra-maturation in the 1980s and for innovative work in the field of cask management since the early 1990s.&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000452', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 13:58:59', '2024-06-10 11:56:57'),
(453, '665736f6c0961', 'PRO000453', 0, 'Glen Moray Sherry Cask Finish', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 28, 25); font-family: din-2014, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.1782px;\">Glen Moray Sherry Cask Finish uses only the finest Oloroso casks to mature this extraordinary single malt. The Elgin Classic&#39;s unmistakable vanilla and light oak is still evident but, with vibrant dried fruit and earthy, nutty notes of the sherry, the finish is multi-faceted.</span></p>', 'Glen Moray Sherry Cask Finish uses only the finest Oloroso casks to mature this extraordinary single malt.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 174, '', 'GLEN MORAY SHERRY CASK FINISH', 'Glen Moray Sherry Cask Finish uses only the finest Oloroso casks to mature this extraordinary single malt.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 28, 25); font-family: din-2014, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.1782px;\">Glen Moray Sherry Cask Finish uses only the finest Oloroso casks to mature this extraordinary single malt. The Elgin Classic&#39;s unmistakable vanilla and light oak is still evident but, with vibrant dried fruit and earthy, nutty notes of the sherry, the finish is multi-faceted.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000453', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 14:08:54', '2024-06-10 11:47:28'),
(454, '66573aab174e0', 'PRO000454', 0, 'Glen Moray Port Cask Finish', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 28, 25); font-family: din-2014, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.1782px;\">This Classic Port Cask Scotch Whisky is a new addition to the Glen Moray Single Malt Family. It has the perfect combination of rich wine flavours with vanilla oak notes because it is matured from the finest American oak barrels then matured for another 8 months in Port pipes. This Whisky is specially selected by the master distiller due to the fact that it is well balanced and full of character.</span></p>', 'This Classic Port Cask Scotch Whisky is a new addition to the Glen Moray Single Malt Family.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 174, '', 'GLEN MORAY PORT CASK FINISH', 'This Classic Port Cask Scotch Whisky is a new addition to the Glen Moray Single Malt Family.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 28, 25); font-family: din-2014, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.1782px;\">This Classic Port Cask Scotch Whisky is a new addition to the Glen Moray Single Malt Family. It has the perfect combination of rich wine flavours with vanilla oak notes because it is matured from the finest American oak barrels then matured for another 8 months in Port pipes. This Whisky is specially selected by the master distiller due to the fact that it is well balanced and full of character.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000454', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 14:24:43', '2024-06-10 11:39:35'),
(455, '66573d43ad060', 'PRO000455', 0, 'Glen Moray Elgin Heritage 18 Years', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 28, 25); font-family: din-2014, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.1782px;\">This Classic Elgin&nbsp;Cask Scotch Whisky is a new addition to the Glen Moray Single Malt Family. It has the perfect combination of rich wine flavours with vanilla oak notes because it is matured from the finest American oak barrels then matured for another 8 months in Port pipes. This Whisky is specially selected by the master distiller due to the fact that it is well balanced and full of character.</span></p>', 'This Classic Elgin Cask Scotch Whisky is a new addition to the Glen Moray Single Malt Family.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 174, '', 'GLEN MORAY ELGIN HERITAGE 18 YEARS', 'This Classic Elgin Cask Scotch Whisky is a new addition to the Glen Moray Single Malt Family.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(25, 28, 25); font-family: din-2014, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 0.1782px;\">This Classic Elgin Cask Scotch Whisky is a new addition to the Glen Moray Single Malt Family. It has the perfect combination of rich wine flavours with vanilla oak notes because it is matured from the finest American oak barrels then matured for another 8 months in Port pipes. This Whisky is specially selected by the master distiller due to the fact that it is well balanced and full of character.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000455', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-29 14:35:47', '2024-06-10 11:30:07'),
(456, '66584832b4525', 'PRO000456', 0, 'Glen Moray Cabernet Cask Finish', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Roboto Slab&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Sweet and full-bodied, the unique character created by finishing in cabernet sauvignon red wine casks is testament to our long-held passion for bringing new flavours to Glen Moray by experimenting with different styles of cask. Our spirit is first matured in American oak then finished in French red wine casks, becoming rich with dark chocolate and intense spice. The rare combination of oak and red wine flavours creates a beautifully rounded whisky with a distinctive character, a delight for both traditional single malt fans and those looking to explore something new.</span></p>', 'Sweet and full-bodied, the unique character created by finishing in cabernet sauvignon red wine casks', 15, '', NULL, 35, 174, '', 'GLEN MORAY CABERNET CASK FINISH', 'Sweet and full-bodied, the unique character created by finishing in cabernet sauvignon red wine casks', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(45, 45, 45); font-family: &quot;Roboto Slab&quot;, serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: center;\">Sweet and full-bodied, the unique character created by finishing in cabernet sauvignon red wine casks is testament to our long-held passion for bringing new flavours to Glen Moray by experimenting with different styles of cask. Our spirit is first matured in American oak then finished in French red wine casks, becoming rich with dark chocolate and intense spice. The rare combination of oak and red wine flavours creates a beautifully rounded whisky with a distinctive character, a delight for both traditional single malt fans and those looking to explore something new.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000456', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 09:34:42', '2024-06-10 11:15:43'),
(457, '66584a6bdd25a', 'PRO000457', 0, 'Glen Moray Chardonnay Cask Finish', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\">Glen Moray Chardonnay Cask Finish is double-matured, first in American oak barrels that previously aged bourbon, and then finished for eight months in Chardonnay casks, infusing the spirit with dried fruit sweetness and subtle spice, it adds. A perfect balance of caramelized fruit, butterscotch and lingering notes of toasted oats. A fresh clean nose with hints of apples, pear drops, fresh key lime pie and bubblegum fading to a cinnamon sugar aroma</span></p>', 'Glen Moray Chardonnay Cask Finish is double-matured, first in American oak barrels', 15, '', NULL, 35, 174, '', 'GLEN MORAY CHARDONNAY CASK FINISH', 'Glen Moray Chardonnay Cask Finish is double-matured, first in American oak barrels', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;Avenir Next&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\">Glen Moray Chardonnay Cask Finish is double-matured, first in American oak barrels that previously aged bourbon, and then finished for eight months in Chardonnay casks, infusing the spirit with dried fruit sweetness and subtle spice, it adds. A perfect balance of caramelized fruit, butterscotch and lingering notes of toasted oats. A fresh clean nose with hints of apples, pear drops, fresh key lime pie and bubblegum fading to a cinnamon sugar aroma</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000457', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 09:44:11', '2024-06-10 11:18:40');
INSERT INTO `product` (`id`, `uniqid`, `product_item_id`, `supplier_id`, `product_name`, `description`, `short_description`, `category_id`, `product_image`, `images`, `subcategory_id`, `brand_id`, `video`, `product_name_fr`, `short_description_fr`, `page_content_fr`, `product_qty`, `tech_data_sheet`, `retail_price`, `discount_price`, `is_admin_approve`, `most_view`, `is_product_bestseller`, `sku`, `average_rating`, `offer`, `status`, `in_store`, `in_online`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(458, '66584bf923f9f', 'PRO000458', 0, 'Glen Moray Peated Single Malt Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Noah; font-size: 16px;\">Balancing smoky intensity with our classic Speyside smoothness, this dram is a fascinating introduction to peated whiskies. It begins with barley which, unusually for Glen Moray, is dried in a peat-fired kiln, for hints of smoke. Uniting this peated barley with our traditional malted barley, our craftsmen distill a lightly peated spirit threaded with distinctive campfire notes. Aged in American oak casks for undertones of vanilla and oak, this smoky single malt reveals a new dimension to Glen Moray, intriguing long-time whisky fans and those new to single malt.</span></p>', 'Balancing smoky intensity with our classic Speyside smoothness, this dram is a fascinating introduction to peated whiskies.', 15, '', NULL, 35, 174, '', 'GLEN MORAY PEATED SINGLE MALT WHISKY', 'Balancing smoky intensity with our classic Speyside smoothness, this dram is a fascinating introduction to peated whiskies.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Noah; font-size: 16px;\">Balancing smoky intensity with our classic Speyside smoothness, this dram is a fascinating introduction to peated whiskies. It begins with barley which, unusually for Glen Moray, is dried in a peat-fired kiln, for hints of smoke. Uniting this peated barley with our traditional malted barley, our craftsmen distill a lightly peated spirit threaded with distinctive campfire notes. Aged in American oak casks for undertones of vanilla and oak, this smoky single malt reveals a new dimension to Glen Moray, intriguing long-time whisky fans and those new to single malt.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000458', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 09:50:49', '2024-06-10 11:24:07'),
(459, '665854a6ee503', 'PRO000459', 0, 'Black Dog Triple Gold Reserve', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Jost, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Black Dog Triple Gold Reserve is a smooth, distinctive blend of rare grain and malt whiskies that captures the richness of India&rsquo;s great tradition of malt whiskies. Noted for its robust, complex taste, this 90 proof blend is a smooth, golden whiskey with hints of oak, smoke, and spice.</span></p>', 'Black Dog Triple Gold Reserve is a smooth, distinctive blend of rare grain and malt whiskies', 15, '', NULL, 48, 12, '', 'Black Dog Triple Gold Reserve', 'Black Dog Triple Gold Reserve is a smooth, distinctive blend of rare grain and malt whiskies', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Jost, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">Black Dog Triple Gold Reserve is a smooth, distinctive blend of rare grain and malt whiskies that captures the richness of India&rsquo;s great tradition of malt whiskies. Noted for its robust, complex taste, this 90 proof blend is a smooth, golden whiskey with hints of oak, smoke, and spice.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000459', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 10:27:50', '2024-05-30 10:28:22'),
(460, '66585cfda33e7', 'PRO000460', 0, 'Black & White', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Harmonia Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.425px;\">Black &amp; White Blended Scotch Whisky was first produced in 1884. It contains 60-65 percent grain whiskies including Port Dundas and Cameronbridge.</span></p>', 'Black & White Blended Scotch Whisky was first produced in 1884', 15, '', NULL, 48, 22, '', 'Black & White', 'Black & White Blended Scotch Whisky was first produced in 1884', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Harmonia Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.425px;\">Black &amp; White Blended Scotch Whisky was first produced in 1884. It contains 60-65 percent grain whiskies including Port Dundas and Cameronbridge.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000460', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 11:03:25', '2024-06-07 14:39:04'),
(461, '66585fae86887', 'PRO000461', 0, 'Black & White', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 115, 129); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">This high-quality blended Scotch whisky is produced to appeal to a large audience. It is now well-known all over the world for its signature taste. This whisky is best served neat over ice and is delicious when added to your favourite mixer.</span></p>', 'This high-quality blended Scotch whisky is produced to appeal to a large audience.', 15, '', NULL, 48, 22, '', 'Black & White', 'This high-quality blended Scotch whisky is produced to appeal to a large audience.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(99, 115, 129); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">This high-quality blended Scotch whisky is produced to appeal to a large audience. It is now well-known all over the world for its signature taste. This whisky is best served neat over ice and is delicious when added to your favourite mixer.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'LQ000461', 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 11:14:54', '2024-05-30 11:14:54'),
(462, '66586c5ed0b6c', 'PRO000462', 0, 'Monkey Shoulder', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 114, 121); font-family: &quot;DIN Next&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Monkey Shoulder is a premium Scotch Whisky that is steeped in history and culture and to this day is still tended by hand by the experienced Malt Men of Speyside. A smooth and rich &#39;triple&#39; malt Scotch (a world first!) that has been blended from three of Speyside&#39;s finest single malts and using batches from only 27 casks to produce this fine malt whisky. A delightful nose of sherry, cinnamon baked pear, butterscotch, barley, strawberry and Bourbon vanilla which are all complemented by tangy, sweet nut, citrus, mint, oak and orange peel flavours.</span></p>', 'Monkey Shoulder is a premium Scotch Whisky that is steeped in history and culture', 15, '', NULL, 48, 48, '', 'MONKEY SHOULDER 700 ML', 'Monkey Shoulder is a premium Scotch Whisky that is steeped in history and culture', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 114, 121); font-family: &quot;DIN Next&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Monkey Shoulder is a premium Scotch Whisky that is steeped in history and culture and to this day is still tended by hand by the experienced Malt Men of Speyside. A smooth and rich &#39;triple&#39; malt Scotch (a world first!) that has been blended from three of Speyside&#39;s finest single malts and using batches from only 27 casks to produce this fine malt whisky. A delightful nose of sherry, cinnamon baked pear, butterscotch, barley, strawberry and Bourbon vanilla which are all complemented by tangy, sweet nut, citrus, mint, oak and orange peel flavours.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000462', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:09:02', '2024-05-31 12:13:46'),
(463, '66586dfc2eedc', 'PRO000463', 0, 'Chivas Regal 12 Years', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 45, 109); font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.75px;\">This 12 year old scotch whisky has been perfected to be smoother than a surfer in a barrel. This blended scotch whisky offers a tidal wave of Strathisla malt and grain, and blockbuster taste notes from luxurious honey and vanilla to ripe apple. It&rsquo;s our warm, generous dram that&rsquo;s born to thrill, and to steals hearts. Because success is a blend, in life and in scotch.Chivas, the original luxury blended scotch whisky, brings together the best malt and grain whiskies. Each component of malt, grain and whisky is special and unique, and when blended together they create something extraordinary.</span></p>', 'This 12 year old scotch whisky has been perfected to be smoother than a surfer in a barrel.', 15, '', NULL, 48, 27, '', 'CHIVAS REGAL 12 YEARS', 'This 12 year old scotch whisky has been perfected to be smoother than a surfer in a barrel.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 45, 109); font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.75px;\">This 12 year old scotch whisky has been perfected to be smoother than a surfer in a barrel. This blended scotch whisky offers a tidal wave of Strathisla malt and grain, and blockbuster taste notes from luxurious honey and vanilla to ripe apple. It&rsquo;s our warm, generous dram that&rsquo;s born to thrill, and to steals hearts. Because success is a blend, in life and in scotch.Chivas, the original luxury blended scotch whisky, brings together the best malt and grain whiskies. Each component of malt, grain and whisky is special and unique, and when blended together they create something extraordinary.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000463', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:15:56', '2024-05-31 12:12:14'),
(464, '66586eccdf87d', 'PRO000464', 0, 'Chivas Regal 18 Years 40%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 45, 109); font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.75px;\">This 12 year old scotch whisky has been perfected to be smoother than a surfer in a barrel. This blended scotch whisky offers a tidal wave of Strathisla malt and grain, and blockbuster taste notes from luxurious honey and vanilla to ripe apple. It&rsquo;s our warm, generous dram that&rsquo;s born to thrill, and to steals hearts. Because success is a blend, in life and in scotch.Chivas, the original luxury blended scotch whisky, brings together the best malt and grain whiskies. Each component of malt, grain and whisky is special and unique, and when blended together they create something extraordinary.</span></p>', 'This 12 year old scotch whisky has been perfected to be smoother than a surfer in a barrel.', 15, '', NULL, 48, 27, '', 'CHIVAS REGAL 18 YEARS 40%', 'This 12 year old scotch whisky has been perfected to be smoother than a surfer in a barrel.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(82, 45, 109); font-family: &quot;Century Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.75px;\">This 12 year old scotch whisky has been perfected to be smoother than a surfer in a barrel. This blended scotch whisky offers a tidal wave of Strathisla malt and grain, and blockbuster taste notes from luxurious honey and vanilla to ripe apple. It&rsquo;s our warm, generous dram that&rsquo;s born to thrill, and to steals hearts. Because success is a blend, in life and in scotch.Chivas, the original luxury blended scotch whisky, brings together the best malt and grain whiskies. Each component of malt, grain and whisky is special and unique, and when blended together they create something extraordinary.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000464', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:19:24', '2024-05-31 12:12:58'),
(465, '66586f8c1beb4', 'PRO000465', 0, 'Chivas Regal 13 Years- Extra 40%', '<p>Chivas Extra 13-year-old&nbsp;Oloroso Sherry Cash, is a rich combination of sweet ripe pears, cinnamon candies and crunchy sweet almonds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This whisky is the fruit of the aging of the classic Chivas for 13 years in Oloroso sherry barrels, giving a rich finish with intense flavours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A nice soft and easy to sip blend with beautiful and sweet Oloroso sherry influences!</p>', 'Chivas Extra 13-year-old Oloroso Sherry Cash, is a rich combination of sweet ripe pears', 15, '', NULL, 48, 27, '', 'CHIVAS REGAL 13 YEARS- EXTRA 40%', 'Chivas Extra 13-year-old Oloroso Sherry Cash, is a rich combination of sweet ripe pears', '<p>Chivas Extra 13-year-old&nbsp;Oloroso Sherry Cash, is a rich combination of sweet ripe pears, cinnamon candies and crunchy sweet almonds.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This whisky is the fruit of the aging of the classic Chivas for 13 years in Oloroso sherry barrels, giving a rich finish with intense flavours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A nice soft and easy to sip blend with beautiful and sweet Oloroso sherry influences!</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000465', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:22:36', '2024-05-31 12:09:45'),
(466, '6658705c213be', 'PRO000466', 0, 'Chivas 18 Years Japanese Oak', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Each drop of the Chivas Regal 18 year Old Blended Scotch whisky has been finished in Japanese Oak casks, a rarity even amongst Japanese whiskies. These remarkable casks are made using delicate Japanese Mizunara Oak that are up to 200 years old. Making them not only difficult to source but also difficult to work with.This exquisite blend is non-chill filtered to maintain its deep amber hue and bottles at a special strength of 48% ABV.</span></p>', 'Each drop of the Chivas Regal 18 year Old Blended Scotch whisky has been finished in Japanese Oak casks', 15, '', NULL, 48, 27, '', 'CHIVAS 18 YEARS JAPANESE OAK', 'Each drop of the Chivas Regal 18 year Old Blended Scotch whisky has been finished in Japanese Oak casks', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(72, 72, 72); font-family: Karla, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\">Each drop of the Chivas Regal 18 year Old Blended Scotch whisky has been finished in Japanese Oak casks, a rarity even amongst Japanese whiskies. These remarkable casks are made using delicate Japanese Mizunara Oak that are up to 200 years old. Making them not only difficult to source but also difficult to work with.This exquisite blend is non-chill filtered to maintain its deep amber hue and bottles at a special strength of 48% ABV.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000466', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:26:04', '2024-05-31 12:08:20'),
(467, '66587167e6cdb', 'PRO000467', 0, 'J&B Blended Scotch Whisky', '<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-family: Lato; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>J&amp;B Rare Blended Scotch Whisky 1 litre&nbsp;​​</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-family: Lato; font-size: 16px;\">Justerini and Brooks classic dram enjoyed by &quot;Mac&quot; R.J MacReady while battling The Thing!&nbsp;</p>', 'Justerini and Brooks classic dram enjoyed by \"Mac\" R.J MacReady while battling The Thing!', 15, '', NULL, 48, 175, '', 'J&B BLENDED SCOTCH WHISKY', 'Justerini and Brooks classic dram enjoyed by \"Mac\" R.J MacReady while battling The Thing!', '<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-family: Lato; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>J&amp;B Rare Blended Scotch Whisky 1 litre&nbsp;​​</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px; color: rgb(48, 48, 48); font-family: Lato; font-size: 16px;\">Justerini and Brooks classic dram enjoyed by &quot;Mac&quot; R.J MacReady while battling The Thing!&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000467', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:30:31', '2024-05-31 12:05:55'),
(468, '6658722e5b2ab', 'PRO000468', 0, 'Chivas Regal Icon', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75); font-family: Questrial, sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; letter-spacing: 0.63px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Only released in limited quantities each year, Chivas Regal The Icon is the pinnacle of the Chivas Regal range. A deep, complex blend of more than 20 of Scotland&rsquo;s rarest whiskies, it includes some from distilleries now lost forever. The taste is full and fruity, with flavours of sweet orange, peaches in syrup and vanilla in abundance. The sweet whisky flavours are balanced to perfection by the hazelnut flavours coming from the cask. A skilfully balanced blend, with a long, luscious and sweet finish, presented by Colin Scott in a hand-crafted crystal decanter, it is a symbol of luxury for a new era.</span></p>', 'Only released in limited quantities each year, Chivas Regal The Icon is the pinnacle of the Chivas Regal range.', 15, '', NULL, 48, 27, '', 'CHIVAS REGAL ICON', 'Only released in limited quantities each year, Chivas Regal The Icon is the pinnacle of the Chivas Regal range.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75); font-family: Questrial, sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; letter-spacing: 0.63px; background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Only released in limited quantities each year, Chivas Regal The Icon is the pinnacle of the Chivas Regal range. A deep, complex blend of more than 20 of Scotland&rsquo;s rarest whiskies, it includes some from distilleries now lost forever. The taste is full and fruity, with flavours of sweet orange, peaches in syrup and vanilla in abundance. The sweet whisky flavours are balanced to perfection by the hazelnut flavours coming from the cask. A skilfully balanced blend, with a long, luscious and sweet finish, presented by Colin Scott in a hand-crafted crystal decanter, it is a symbol of luxury for a new era.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000468', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:33:50', '2024-05-31 12:07:28'),
(469, '665873b14558a', 'PRO000469', 0, 'Label 5 Whisky 40%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 21, 22); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">LABEL5 is a Modern Classic, An international and high quality Scotch Whisky, affordable, associated to modernity and conviviality. LABEL 5 invites you to a world tour by night to share a convivial time of Scotch Whisky tasting LABEL 5 Classic Black is a great smooth, subtly smoky and delicately fruity Blended Scotch Whisky, with a generous ration of Speyside malt.</span></p>', 'LABEL5 is a Modern Classic, An international and high quality Scotch Whisky', 15, '', NULL, 48, 176, '', 'LABEL 5 WHISKY 40% 1.5LTR', 'LABEL5 is a Modern Classic, An international and high quality Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 21, 22); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">LABEL5 is a Modern Classic, An international and high quality Scotch Whisky, affordable, associated to modernity and conviviality. LABEL 5 invites you to a world tour by night to share a convivial time of Scotch Whisky tasting LABEL 5 Classic Black is a great smooth, subtly smoky and delicately fruity Blended Scotch Whisky, with a generous ration of Speyside malt.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000469', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:40:17', '2024-05-31 12:04:58'),
(470, '665877030b239', 'PRO000470', 0, 'Label 5 Whisky 40%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 21, 22); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">LABEL5 is a Modern Classic, An international and high quality Scotch Whisky, affordable, associated to modernity and conviviality. LABEL 5 invites you to a world tour by night to share a convivial time of Scotch Whisky tasting LABEL 5 Classic Black is a great smooth, subtly smoky and delicately fruity Blended Scotch Whisky, with a generous ration of Speyside malt.</span></p>', 'LABEL5 is a Modern Classic, An international and high quality Scotch Whisky', 15, '', NULL, 48, 176, '', 'LABEL 5 WHISKY 40%', 'LABEL5 is a Modern Classic, An international and high quality Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 21, 22); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">LABEL5 is a Modern Classic, An international and high quality Scotch Whisky, affordable, associated to modernity and conviviality. LABEL 5 invites you to a world tour by night to share a convivial time of Scotch Whisky tasting LABEL 5 Classic Black is a great smooth, subtly smoky and delicately fruity Blended Scotch Whisky, with a generous ration of Speyside malt.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000470', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 12:54:27', '2024-06-11 12:49:24'),
(471, '66587d7467dbb', 'PRO000471', 0, 'Label 5 Whisky 40% Classic Black', '<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Noah; margin-bottom: 0.7em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important;\">Label&nbsp;5 Classic Black is a Blended Scotch Whisky which is delightfully smooth with subtle smoke influences and a delicate fruity character. Speyside malts are the backbone to this blend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Noah; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important;\">Delicate notes of fruits laced with peat and freshly baked shortbread. A delightfully balanced blend, initial flavors of fruit and vanilla followed by a slight smoky sensation emerging. Long and smooth with a hint of wood smoke.</p>', 'Label 5 Classic Black is a Blended Scotch Whisky which is delightfully smooth with subtle smoke influences', 15, '', NULL, 48, 176, '', 'LABEL 5 WHISKY 40% CLASSIC BLACK', 'Label 5 Classic Black is a Blended Scotch Whisky which is delightfully smooth with subtle smoke influences', '<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Noah; margin-bottom: 0.7em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important;\">Label&nbsp;5 Classic Black is a Blended Scotch Whisky which is delightfully smooth with subtle smoke influences and a delicate fruity character. Speyside malts are the backbone to this blend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin-top: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: Noah; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important;\">Delicate notes of fruits laced with peat and freshly baked shortbread. A delightfully balanced blend, initial flavors of fruit and vanilla followed by a slight smoky sensation emerging. Long and smooth with a hint of wood smoke.</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000471', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-30 13:21:56', '2024-06-11 12:27:25'),
(472, '6659949e94087', 'PRO000472', 0, 'Vat 69 Blended Scotch Whisky', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">It dates back to 1882 and is&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(211, 227, 253) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 50%); background-position: 0% 0px; background-size: 200% 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(4, 12, 40); animation: 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.05, 0.7, 0.1, 1) 0.25s 1 normal forwards running highlight; font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">a blend of over 40 malt and grain whiskies matured in oak casks</span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">. Its name comes from the 69th vat created by William Sanderson. It has an alcohol content of 40%, comes in a 1L bottle, and is an international whiskey produced in Scotland.</span></p>', 'It dates back to 1882 and is a blend of over 40 malt and grain whiskies matured in oak casks.', 15, '', NULL, 48, 177, '', 'VAT 69 BLENDED SCOTCH WHISKY', 'It dates back to 1882 and is a blend of over 40 malt and grain whiskies matured in oak casks.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">It dates back to 1882 and is&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(211, 227, 253) 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 50%); background-position: 0% 0px; background-size: 200% 100%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; color: rgb(4, 12, 40); animation: 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.05, 0.7, 0.1, 1) 0.25s 1 normal forwards running highlight; font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">a blend of over 40 malt and grain whiskies matured in oak casks</span><span style=\"color: rgb(32, 33, 36); font-family: &quot;Google Sans&quot;, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">. Its name comes from the 69th vat created by William Sanderson. It has an alcohol content of 40%, comes in a 1L bottle, and is an international whiskey produced in Scotland.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000472', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-31 09:13:02', '2024-06-11 12:22:19'),
(473, '6659956f0fae8', 'PRO000473', 0, 'High Commissioner', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Karla, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">High Commissioner Blended Scotch Whisky was first founded in 1856 and opened for the first time in 1866. It&#39;s known for its balance of flavour, making softly fruity whisky with a touch of caramel and a whisper of peat. Originally founded by the Bulloch family, this blended malt whisky has kept its original recipe.</span></p>', 'High Commissioner Blended Scotch Whisky was first founded in 1856 and opened for the first time in 1866.', 15, '', NULL, 48, 178, '', 'HIGH COMMISSIONER', 'High Commissioner Blended Scotch Whisky was first founded in 1856 and opened for the first time in 1866.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Karla, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">High Commissioner Blended Scotch Whisky was first founded in 1856 and opened for the first time in 1866. It&#39;s known for its balance of flavour, making softly fruity whisky with a touch of caramel and a whisper of peat. Originally founded by the Bulloch family, this blended malt whisky has kept its original recipe.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000473', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-05-31 09:16:31', '2024-06-11 12:17:12'),
