(527, '665e0012a4736', 'PRO000527', 0, 'Hennessy VS With Box NBA', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 68, 69); font-family: system, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Oxygen, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.35px;\">Cognac has an exciting aroma with dominant notes of vanilla and oak, light nuance berries, followed by gentle shades of hazelnut and colors.</span></p>', 'Cognac has an exciting aroma with dominant notes of vanilla and oak, light nuance berries', 21, '', NULL, 43, 72, '', 'Hennessy VS With Box NBA', 'Cognac has an exciting aroma with dominant notes of vanilla and oak, light nuance berries', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 68, 69); font-family: system, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Oxygen, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.35px;\">Cognac has an exciting aroma with dominant notes of vanilla and oak, light nuance berries, followed by gentle shades of hazelnut and colors.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'LQ000527', 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-03 17:40:34', '2024-06-03 17:40:34'),
(528, '665e028265919', 'PRO000528', 0, 'Hennessy Vsop', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 68, 69); font-family: system, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Oxygen, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.35px;\">Cognac is a multi-faceted taste with a rich, voluminous texture and rich flavor of different flavors, in a frame which contains notes of early fruit, shaded light freshness. Pleasant aftertaste with a hint of vanilla, which creates a sense of completeness and richness of taste.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 68, 69); font-family: system, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Oxygen, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.35px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'Cognac is a multi-faceted taste with a rich, voluminous texture and rich flavor of different flavors', 21, '', NULL, 43, 72, '', 'Hennessy Vsop', 'Cognac is a multi-faceted taste with a rich, voluminous texture and rich flavor of different flavors', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 68, 69); font-family: system, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Oxygen, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.35px;\">Cognac is a multi-faceted taste with a rich, voluminous texture and rich flavor of different flavors, in a frame which contains notes of early fruit, shaded light freshness. Pleasant aftertaste with a hint of vanilla, which creates a sense of completeness and richness of taste.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(70, 68, 69); font-family: system, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;Segoe WP&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, Oxygen, Cantarell, &quot;Fira Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, &quot;Droid Sans&quot;, Tahoma, &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.35px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, 'LQ000528', 0, 0, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-03 17:50:58', '2024-06-03 17:53:14'),
(529, '665e0562ca075', 'PRO000529', 0, 'St Remy Vsop', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Thanks to a longer aging, in small barrels, ST REMY Authentic French Brandy VSOP acquires a magnificent amber color with golden highlights.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">The blend of the fruitiness and the acid drop of the eau-de-vie reveal notes of cherries and raspberries with touches of vanilla and oak.&nbsp;</p>', 'Thanks to a longer aging, in small barrels, ST REMY Authentic French Brandy VSOP', 21, '', NULL, 43, 72, '', 'St Remy Vsop', 'Thanks to a longer aging, in small barrels, ST REMY Authentic French Brandy VSOP', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Thanks to a longer aging, in small barrels, ST REMY Authentic French Brandy VSOP acquires a magnificent amber color with golden highlights.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">The blend of the fruitiness and the acid drop of the eau-de-vie reveal notes of cherries and raspberries with touches of vanilla and oak.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'LQ000529', 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-03 18:03:14', '2024-06-03 18:03:14'),
(530, '665e09768eed1', 'PRO000530', 0, 'Martell Blue Swift 40%', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(2, 9, 18, 0.75); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; letter-spacing: 0.63px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Martell Blue Swift Spirit is a VSOP cognac that, after being traditionally distilled, undergoes additional maturation in American bourbon casks. This unique double aging process gives rise to notes of vanilla, ripe fruits, sweet spices, and toasted oak, offering a dynamic and daring taste experience with a long and balanced finish.</span></p>', 'Martell Blue Swift Spirit is a VSOP cognac that, after being traditionally distilled', 21, '', NULL, 43, 46, '', 'Martell Blue Swift 40%', 'Martell Blue Swift Spirit is a VSOP cognac that, after being traditionally distilled', '<p><span style=\"color: rgba(2, 9, 18, 0.75); font-family: Quicksand, sans-serif; font-size: 16.8px; letter-spacing: 0.63px; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Martell Blue Swift Spirit is a VSOP cognac that, after being traditionally distilled, undergoes additional maturation in American bourbon casks. This unique double aging process gives rise to notes of vanilla, ripe fruits, sweet spices, and toasted oak, offering a dynamic and daring taste experience with a long and balanced finish.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'LQ000530', 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-03 18:20:38', '2024-06-03 18:20:38'),
(531, '665edf9c9e86e', 'PRO000531', 0, 'Martell Cognac Vsop', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 21, 22); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Established in 1715, Martell is the oldest of the great cognac houses. Martell VSOP is a cognac that is made with skilfully blended, mature eaux-de-vie from the four finest growths of the Cognac region. Aged in French oak casks, those eaux-de-vie are selected by the cellar master to yield a perfect balance of freshness and crisp-edged sweetness.</span></p>', 'Established in 1715, Martell is the oldest of the great cognac houses.', 21, '', NULL, 43, 46, '', 'Martell Cognac Vsop', 'Established in 1715, Martell is the oldest of the great cognac houses.', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(17, 21, 22); font-family: Ubuntu, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Established in 1715, Martell is the oldest of the great cognac houses. Martell VSOP is a cognac that is made with skilfully blended, mature eaux-de-vie from the four finest growths of the Cognac region. Aged in French oak casks, those eaux-de-vie are selected by the cellar master to yield a perfect balance of freshness and crisp-edged sweetness.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, 0, NULL, 0, NULL, NULL, 'LQ000531', 0, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, '2024-06-04 09:34:20', '2024-06-04 09:34:20');
